%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20PM%20Modi%20Has%20Failed%20Manipur%20Constitutionally%2C%20Politically%2C%20Morally%3A%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Former%20Mizoram%20VP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18175028%2Fkt-18-blank.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20R.%20Vanramchhuanga%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-bjp-vice-president-resigns-says-manipur-union-govts-supported-demolition-of-churches%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20party%20on%20July%2013%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9Can%20anti-Christian%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20has%20said%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfailure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVanramchhuanga%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%20is%20head%20of%20the%20government%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20constitutionally%2C%20politically%2C%20and%20morally%20responsible%20to%20safeguard%20his%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20failed%20in%20all%20three%20aspects%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2033-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Vanramchhuanga%20raised%20a%20series%20of%20questions%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20asking%20why%20he%20is%20keeping%20mum%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20he%20declare%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%3F%20Why%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20he%20safeguard%20and%20comfort%20the%20tribal%20people%3F%20Why%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20he%20safeguard%20Christians%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVanramchhuanga%20then%20appeared%20to%20answer%20the%20questions%20himself%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%2C%20I%20say%2C%20he%20has%20totally%20failed%20to%20protect%20his%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20directly%20held%20responsible%20both%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20for%20their%20failure%20to%20prevent%20Christian%20churches%20from%20being%20burnt%20to%20ashes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20their%20failure%20to%20protect%20the%20Kuki%20Christian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20irresponsible%20people%20behind%20this%20conflict%20are%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20They%20failed%20to%20protect%20the%20victims%2C%20the%20Christians%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20agreed%20that%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20is%20guilty%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdereliction%20of%20duty%E2%80%9D%20and%20of%20failing%20to%20fulfil%20his%20%E2%80%9Cmoral%20responsibility%E2%80%9D%20as%20home%20minister.%20He%20added%20that%20Shah%20has%20%E2%80%9Cfailed%20his%20oath%20taken%20on%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20resignation%20letter%20dated%20July%2013%2C%20he%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9C357%20Christian%20churches%2C%20pastor%20quarters%20and%20office%20buildings%20belonging%20to%20different%20churches%20were%2C%20so%20far%2C%20burnt%20to%20ashes%20by%20Meitei%20militants.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20he%20said%20not%20only%20does%20he%20stand%20by%20this%20%5Bclaim%5D%2C%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Ccertain%E2%80%9D%20of%20it.%20He%20said%20although%20he%E2%80%99s%20not%20in%20Manipur%2C%20this%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cconfirmed%E2%80%9D%20by%20various%20sources%20and%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20in%20all%20probability%2C%20the%20actual%20burning%20was%20done%20by%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20after%20his%20resignation%2C%20he%20had%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20%E2%80%9Can%20anti-Christian%20party.%E2%80%9D%20He%20said%20he%20stands%20by%20that%20and%20exp