tition%20will%20be%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-police-brij-bhushan-bjp-mp-wrestlers-chargesheet%5C%22%3Ehad%20filed%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20charge-sheet%20against%20the%20six-time%20MP%20on%20June%2015%20under%20sections%20354%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20woman%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty)%2C%20354A%20(sexual%20harassment)%2C%20354D%20(stalking)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETomar%20was%20charged%20with%20offences%20under%20IPC%20sections%20109%20(abetment%20of%20any%20offence%2C%20if%20the%20act%20abetted%20is%20committed%20in%20consequence%2C%20and%20where%20no%20express%20provision%20is%20made%20for%20its%20punishment)%2C%20354%2C%20354A%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20case%20registered%20by%20six%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20another%20first%20information%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwrestlers-protest-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-withdraw-complaint-minor-pocso%5C%22%3Ewas%20registered%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Singh%20by%20a%20minor%20grappler%2C%20which%20was%20registered%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act.%20She%20was%20among%20the%20seven%20female%20wrestlers%20who%20had%20accused%20Singh%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20been%20the%20primary%20concern%20of%20protesting%20wrestlers%20that%20a%20man%20booked%20under%20POCSO%2C%20which%20calls%20for%20immediate%20action%2C%20had%20not%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20against%20Singh%20include%20inappropriate%20touching%2C%20groping%2C%20stalking%20and%20intimidation%20by%20him%20at%20different%20times%20and%20places%20over%20a%20decade.%20Other%20allegations%20against%20him%20include%20dictatorial%20functioning%20and%20financial%20irregulariti