nities%20and%20chose%20to%20remain%20confined%20to%20Kerala.%20He%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20ambitious%20in%20a%20reckless%20fashion.%20To%20some%20extent%2C%20he%20was%20self-effacing%20and%20friends%20with%20leaders%20of%20all%20political%20parties.%20A%20quintessential%20Kerala%20politician%20of%20a%20generation%20that%20was%20catapulted%20into%20mainstream%20politics%20through%20student%20activism%2C%20Chandy%E2%80%99s%20demise%20leaves%20a%20profound%20void%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20political%20landscape%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20needs%20peaceniks%20like%20him%20the%20most.%20Besides%20being%20an%20astute%20and%20pragmatic%20politician%2C%20he%20was%20destined%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20amiable%20and%20popular%20faces%20in%20state%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20quality%20of%20Oommen%20Chandy%20was%20his%20phenomenal%20presence%20amongst%20the%20people%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20always%20amidst%20the%20adoring%20masses.%20He%20dwelled%20among%20the%20masses%20and%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20occasion%20when%20he%20distanced%20from%20them.%20The%20way%20he%20connected%20with%20individuals%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20has%20become%20part%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20political%20folklore.%20With%20other%20prominent%20Congress%20leaders%20like%20K.%20Karunakaran%20and%20A.K.%20Antony%20retired%20from%20public%20life%2C%20Chandy%E2%80%99s%20demise%20means%20curtains%20for%20a%20grand%20era%20of%20Congress%20politics%20and%20the%20end%20of%20the%20titans%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresenting%20a%20constituency%20consecutively%20for%20more%20than%20five%20decades%20is%20a%20remarkable%20feat%20very%20few%20could%20achieve%20in%20the%20world.%20Elected%20to%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20of%20Kerala%20from%20Puthuppally%2C%20a%20suburb%20of%20Kottayam%2C%20in%201970%2C%20Chandy%E2%80%99s%20upward%20trajectory%20remained%20unchallenged%20until%20his%20death.%20Interestingly%2C%20during%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20rivals%20used%20to%20skip%20campaigning%20in%20this%20constituency%20so%20as%20not%20to%20waste%20their%20time%20on%20what%20was%20Chandy%E2%80%99s%20turf.%20While%20it%20is%20customary%20to%20highlight%20his%20administrative%20acumen%20as%20a%20two-time%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%2C%20Chandy%E2%80%99s%20remarkable%20ability%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20masses%20outshines%20every%20other%20attribute%20of%20his.%20Half%20in%20jest%2C%20people%20used%20to%20say%20that%20with%20his%20admirers%20and%20visitors%20following%20him%20all%20the%20time%2C%20Chandy%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20moment%20of%20solitude%20to%20go%20to%20the%20toilet%20alone.%20Except%20when%20he%20slept%2C%20which%20was%20only%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20one%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20see%20him%20without%20being%20surrounded%20by%20scores%20of%20people.%20Many%20a%20time%2C%20he%20struggled%20to%20find%20space%20in%20his%20own%20car%20where%20Congressmen%20used%20to%20even%20sit%20on%20the%20lap%20of%20others.%20His%20personal%20and%20political%20lives%20intertwined%20seamlessly%2C%20making%20him%20a%20leader%20whose%20distinction%20between%20the%20two%20realms%20was%20imperceptible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20the%20Congress%20in%20Kerala%20had%20two%20warring%20factions%2C%20one%20led%20by%20K.%20Karunakaran%20and%20the%20other%20by%20A.K.%20Antony.%20Nonetheless%2C%20it%20was%20Chandy%20who%20shouldered%20the%20whole%20burden%20of%20steering%20the%20party%2C%20organisationally%20and%20politically.%20As%20a%20master%20multitasker%2C%20even%20while%20advancing%20the%20Congress%20narrative%2C%20he%20could%20skilfully%20weave%20out%20a%20rainbow%20coalition%20against%20the%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20in%20Kerala.%20This%20writer%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20observing%20and%20interacting%20with%20him%20for%20over%20three%20decades.%20One%20thing%20that%20always%20struck%20me%20was%20his%20innate%20ability%20to%20remain%20unprovoked%20even%20in%20the%20most%20hostile%20moments.%20The%20disarming%20smile%20and%20the%20artificial%20stammer%20served%20as%20his%20natural%20shields%20during%20confrontations.%20The%20late%20E.M.S.%20Namboodiripad%2C%20the%20CPI(M)%20patriarch%2C%20used%20to%20ponder%20over%20what%20to%20say%20next%20by%20employing%20pauses%20between%20sentences%20on%20account%20of%20his%20natural%20stammering.%20Chandy%20recreated%20it%20in%20his%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20be%20at%20his%20aggressive%20best%20at%20one%20moment%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20but%20in%20the%20next%2C%20he%20would%20invariably%20uphold%20the%20golden%20virtues%20of%20rapprochement%2C%20tolerance%20and%20accommodation.%20He%20belonged%20to%20a%20rare%20breed%20of%20politicians%20for%20whom%20there%20were%20no%20enemies%20but%20only%20adversaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20exactly%20did%20he%20lack%20despite%20all%20his%20other%20great%20qualities%3F%20In%20hindsight%2C%20he%20would%20have%20acknowledged%20the%20need%20for%20more%20prudence%20and%20caution%20before%20taking%20decisions.%20The%20way%20in%20which%20he%20struggled%20to%20accommodate%20anyone%20and%20everyone%20had%20a%20disastrous%20effect%20on%20his%20political%20career.%20He%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20good%20care%20of%20his%20health%20as%20he%20tried%20to%20cope%20with%20the%20rapidly%20changing%20dynamics%20of%20Congress%20politics%20and%20was%20always%20reluctant%20to%20shift%20out%20of%20Kerala.%20It%20was%20common%20knowledge%20that%20he%20reluctantly%20took%20up%20the%20charge%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20his%20days%20in%20Delhi%20were%20like%20a%20fish%20out%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandy%20was%20a%20lexicon%20of%20sorts%20for%20the%20average%20Congress%20worker%20to%20pick%20up%20political%20vocabulary%20from.%20He%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%2C%20starting%20with%20student%20politics%20and%20became%20an%20icon%20for%20his%20ardent%20followers.%20His%20simplicity%2C%20attire%2C%20and%20even%20his%20hairstyle%20were%20always%20the%20talk%20of%20the%20town.%20Kerala%20was%20rife%20with%20jokes%20about%20his%20torn%20clothes%20and%20his%20aversion%20to%20combing%20his%20hair.%20During%20an%20interview%2C%20this%20writer%20asked%20him%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20truth%20to%20the%20jokes%20being%20spread%20by%20his%20former%20colleagues%20that%20he%20deliberately%20used%20a%20blade%20to%20tear%20his%20clothes%20and%20deliberately%20rearranged%20his%20hair%20even%20after%20combing%20to%20master%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccarefully%20careless%E2%80%9D%20appearance.%20As%20expected%2C%20he%20just%20laughed%20off%20the%20allegations%20in%20a%20gracious%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20a%20time%20when%20ideological%20positions%20get%20blurred%20and%20leaders%20cross%20over%20at%20ease%2C%20Chandy%20steadfastly%20held%20the%20Congress%20flag%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20bid%20farewell%20to%20this%20seasoned%20leader%2C%20we%20are%20at%20a%20point%20in%20Indian%20history%20where%20bipartisanship%20is%20the%20biggest%20casualty%20of%20an%20authoritarian%20rule.%20He%20was%20a%20votary%20for%20peace%20and%20a%20gentleman-politician%20who%20understood%20the%20role%20of%20love%20in%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20people%20as%20well%20as%20towards%20his%20bitterest%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJohn%20Brittas%20is%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689680275000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18170414%2FF1SUdntaYAQL7Ks.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Foommen-chandy-a-true-leader-of-the-people%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20Kerala%20chief%20minister%20was%20a%20Congress%20stalwart%20and%20an%20undying%20democrat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Foommen-chandy-a-true-leader-of-the-people%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mattel%20hated%20the%201997%20song%20'Barbie%20Girl'%20so%20much%20that%20it%20sued.%20Now%2C%20the%20song%20is%20making%20a%20return%20thanks%20to%20Greta%20Gerwig.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryan%20Gosling%20as%20Ken%20and%20Margot%20Robbie%20as%20Barbie%20in%20%26quot%3BBarbie.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b57cfa64dab3001999f782%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221410%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERyan%20Gosling%20and%20Margot%20Robbie%20as%20Ken%20and%20Barbie%20in%20%26quot%3BBarbie.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Warner%20Bros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAqua's%20chart-topping%201997%20hit%20%26quot%3BBarbie%20Girl%26quot%3B%20called%20the%20doll%20a%20%26quot%3Bblond%20bimbo%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20full%20of%20innuendos.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMattel%20sued%20MCA%20Records%20over%20the%20song%2C%20but%20a%C2%A0judge%20dismissed%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BBarbie%20Girl%26quot%3B%20is%20now%20being%20revived%20in%20Greta%20Gerwig's%20film%20with%20a%20performance%20by%20Nicki%20Minaj%20and%20Ice%20Spice.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBarbie%20Girl%2C%26quot%3B%20by%20Danish-Norwegian%20Europop%20band%20Aqua%2C%20peaked%20at%20number%20seven%20in%20the%20US%20Billboard%20Hot%20100%20in%201997.%20It%20topped%20the%20charts%20from%20the%20UK%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20year%20of%20its%20release%20and%20was%20Belgium's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20180612145841%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ultratop.be%2Fnl%2Fultratop_nineties_500.asp%3Fpage%3D1%5C%22%3Esecond-best%20selling%20single%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20entire%20decade%2C%20behind%20just%20Elton%20John.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Mattel%20%E2%80%94%20which%20manufactures%20Barbie%20%E2%80%94%20hated%20the%20song%2C%20so%20much%20that%20it%20sued%20MCA%20Records%2C%20Aqua's%20American%20record%20label%2C%20which%20later%20became%20part%20of%20Universal%20Music%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBarbie%20Girl%2C%26quot%3B%20from%20Aqua's%20debut%20album%2C%20%26quot%3Bpoked%20fun%20at%20the%20squeaky%20clean%20values%20Barbie%20represents%20as%20well%20as%20the%20kinky%20fantasies%20she%20ignites%2C%26quot%3B%20Orly%20Lobel%20wrote%20in%20her%202018%20book%20%26quot%3BYou%20Don't%20Own%20Me%3A%20The%20Court%20Battles%20That%20Exposed%20Barbie's%20Dark%20Side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20music%20video%20features%20two%20members%20of%20Aqua%20dressed%20as%20Barbie%20and%20Ken%2C%20riding%20round%20in%20a%20pink%20convertible%20and%20frolicking%20in%20Barbie's%20Dreamhouse.%20Lene%20Nystr%C3%B8m%2C%20playing%20Barbie%2C%20sings%20in%20a%20sickly-sweet%2C%20butter-couldn't-melt%20voice%2C%20while%20Ren%C3%A9%20Dif%20sings%20as%20a%20deep-voiced%20Ken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyrics%20include%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20blond%20bimbo%20girl%20in%20a%20fantasy%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BKiss%20me%20here%2C%20touch%20me%20there%2C%20hanky%20panky.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMattel%2C%20understandably%2C%20had%20some%20problems%20with%20this%20portrayal%20of%20its%2011-inch%20doll.%20But%2C%20as%20Lobel%20noted%2C%20Mattel%20couldn't%20sue%20for%20copyright%20infringement%20because%20the%20video%20didn't%20include%20any%20actual%20Barbie%20dolls%20or%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20toy%20giant%20instead%20sued%20MCA%20Records%20for%20using%20the%20trademarked%20word%20%26quot%3BBarbie%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20Mattel%20said%20the%20song%20had%20used%20without%20approval%20and%20could%20lead%20the%20public%20to%20believe%20that%20Mattel%20itself%20had%20produced%20the%20song%2C%20Lobel%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20one%20really%20thought%20that%20the%20tongue-in-cheek%20song%20could%20have%20been%20written%20by%20Mattel%2C%20Lobel%20wrote.%20It%20was%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20a%20parody%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bpoking%20fun%20at%20Barbie%20rather%20than%20trying%20to%20pass%20off%20the%20song%20as%20a%20Mattel%20product.%26quot%3B%20And%20copyrighted%20work%20can%20be%20used%20without%20permission%20if%20it's%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20parody.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20song%20title%20does%20not%20explicitly%20mislead%20as%20to%20the%20source%20of%20the%20work%3B%20it%20does%20not%2C%20explicitly%20or%20otherwise%2C%20suggest%20that%20it%20was%20produced%20by%20Mattel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Judge%20Alex%20Kozinski%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaselaw.findlaw.com%2Fcourt%2Fus-9th-circuit%2F1260576.html%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224396%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Danish%20pop%20group%20Aqua%20at%20the%20Billboard%20Music%20Awards%20at%20the%20MGM%20Grand%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%208th%20December%201997.%20From%20left%20to%20right%2C%20they%20are%20guitarist%20Claus%20Norreen%2C%20keyboardist%20Soren%20Rasted%2C%20and%20vocalists%20Lene%20Nystrom%20and%20Ren%C3%A9%20Dif.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b66d54db902600193565f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223297%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAqua%20at%20the%201997%20Billboard%20Music%20Awards.%3Cp%3EVinnie%20Zuffante%2FMichael%20Ochs%20Archives%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Farchives%2Fla-xpm-1997-sep-06-ca-29293-story.html%5C%22%3Enote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20single's%20CD%20case%20even%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20song%20'Barbie%20Girl'%20is%20a%20social%20comment%20and%20was%20not%20created%20or%20approved%20by%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20doll.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20tongue-in-cheek%2C%26quot%3B%20Nystr%C3%B8m%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollingstone.com%2Fmusic%2Fmusic-features%2Faqua-barbie-girl-oral-history-1319069%2F%5C%22%3ERolling%20Stone%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20song%20in%202022.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20see%20the%20layers%20to%20it%2C%20there's%20all%20the%20layers%20you%20want.%20But%20we%20kind%20of%20took%20the%20piss%20out%20of%20the%20Pamela%20Anderson%20'Baywatch'%20perfect%20picture%20with%20silicon%20boobs.%20We%20wanted%20to%20take%20the%20piss%20out%20of%20that%20kind%20of%20perfect%20girl.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKozinski%20wasn't%20swayed%20by%20Mattel's%20argument%20that%20the%20song%20was%20inappropriate%20and%20damaged%20Barbie's%20reputation%2C%20which%20Lobel%20wrote%20is%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20trademark%20law%2C%20designed%20to%20protect%20consumers%20from%20fraud%20or%20deception.%20Kozinski%20said%20that%20though%20the%20word%20Barbie%20now%20had%20connotations%20with%20both%20the%20doll%20and%20the%20song%2C%20the%20right%20to%20free%20speech%20in%20the%20case%20of%20criticism%20or%20parody%20outweighed%20this%2C%20per%20Lobel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20was%20ultimately%20dismissed.%20%26quot%3BThe%20parties%20are%20advised%20to%20chill%2C%26quot%3B%20Kozinski%20concluded%20in%20his%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20song%20was%20a%20massive%20success%20for%20Aqua%20and%20has%20become%20part%20of%20the%20cultural%20zeitgeist%20of%20the%201990s.%20In%20a%20review%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fworldradiohistory.com%2FArchive-All-Music%2FBillboard%2F90s%2F1997%2FBillboard-1997-08-16.pdf%5C%22%3EBillboard%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time%2C%20it%20was%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Ba%20deliciously%20over-the-top%20send-up%20of%20America's%20most%20beloved%20doll%26quot%3B%20with%20references%20to%20%26quot%3Bthe%20inherent%20misogyny%20of%20Barbie%26quot%3B%20while%20also%20%26quot%3Bgleefully%20verbalizing%20many%20of%20the%20twisted%20things%20people%20secretly%20do%20with%20the%20doll.%26quot%3B%20On%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZyhrYis509A%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20video%20has%201.2%20billion%20views.%20On%20Spotify%2C%20it%20has%20381%20billion%20listens%20%E2%80%93%20over%20four%20times%20more%20than%20Aqua's%20second-most-listened-to%20song.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYears%20later%2C%20Mattel%20even%20bought%20the%20rights%20to%20the%20song%20from%20Aqua%2C%20Lobel%20wrote.%20Mattel%20began%20using%20a%20modified%20song%20in%20promotional%20materials%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.nytimes.com%2Fmediadecoder.blogs.nytimes.com%2F2009%2F08%2F26%2Fyears-later-mattel-embraces-barbie-girl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%202009%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20song%20is%20now%20making%20a%20comeback%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20thanks%20to%20Greta%20Gerwig's%20%26quot%3BBarbie%26quot%3B%20film%2C%20which%20is%20hitting%20cinemas%20this%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBarbie%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20by%20Nicki%20Minaj%2C%20Ice%20Spice%2C%20and%20Aqua%2C%20revives%20%26quot%3BBarbie%20Girl%26quot%3B's%20original%20chorus%2C%20which%20is%20sung%20by%20Nystr%C3%B8m%2C%20alongside%20lyrics%20like%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20ten%2C%20so%20I%20pull%20in%20a%20Ken%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhe%20spank%20me%20when%20I%20get%20bad.%26quot%3B%20It%20already%20has%20more%20than%2048%20million%20listens%20on%20Spotify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbie-girl-mattel-sued-mca-barbie-world-song-aqua-movie-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689680076000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b66c72db902600193565d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarbie-girl-mattel-sued-mca-barbie-world-song-aqua-movie-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aqua's%20chart-topping%201997%20hit%20%26quot%3BBarbie%20Girl%26quot%3B%20called%20the%20doll%20a%20%26quot%3Bblond%20bimbo%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20full%20of%20innuendos.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2