rative%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20department%20said%20in%20its%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDear%20Taxpayers%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnConcerns%20have%20been%20raised%20by%20certain%20NRIs%2F%20OCIs%20regarding%20their%20PANs%20becoming%20inoperative%2C%20although%20they%20are%20exempted%20from%20linking%20their%20PAN%20with%20Aadhaar.%3Cbr%3E%5CnFurther%2C%20PAN%20holders%2C%20whose%20PANs%20have%20been%20rendered%20inoperative%20due%20to%20non-linking%20of%20PAN%20with%20Aadhaar%2C%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Income%20Tax%20India%20(%40IncomeTaxIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIncomeTaxIndia%2Fstatus%2F1681251168276860928%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20then%20gave%20a%20lengthy%20clarification.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BITD%20has%20mapped%20the%20residential%20status%20of%20NRIs%20in%20case%20they%20have%20filed%20the%20ITR%20in%20any%20of%20the%20last%203%20AYs%20or%20they%20have%20intimated%20their%20residential%20status%20to%20the%20Jurisdictional%20Assessing%20Officer%20(JAO).%20The%20PANs%20have%20been%20rendered%20inoperative%2C%20in%20case%20any%20one%20of%20the%20above-mentioned%20criteria%20is%20not%20met%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IT%20department%20said%20in%20the%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PANs%20of%20OCIs%2Fforeign%20citizens%2C%20who%20may%20have%20applied%20for%20PAN%20under%20resident%20status%20and%20have%20not%20corrected%2Fupdated%20their%20residential%20status%20to%20the%20Jurisdictional%20Assessing%20Officer%20(JAO)%20or%20have%20not%20filed%20ITR%20in%20any%20of%20the%20last%203%20AYs%2C%20have%20been%20rendered%20inoperative%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20tweet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20then%20asked%20the%20NRIs%20and%20OCIs%20to%20update%20their%20residential%20status%20on%20the%20income%20tax%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20July%201%2C%20the%20PAN%20cards%20of%20those%20individuals%20who%20did%20not%20link%20them%20with%20Aadhaar%20were%20made%20inoperative.%20The%20income%20tax%20department%20had%20earlier%20mentioned%20that%20it%20will%20take%20action%20against%20such%20individuals%2C%20which%20include%20higher%20TDS%20and%20TCS%20rates%20and%20no%20refund%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689679140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Fs8unk5og_pan-card-ndtv_625x300_19_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fincome-tax-department-explains-why-pan-cards-of-some-nris-were-made-inoperative-4218621%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20department%20then%20asked%20the%20NRIs%20and%20OCIs%20to%20update%20their%20residential%20status%20on%20the%20income%20tax%20website.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fincome-tax-department-explains-why-pan-cards-of-some-nris-were-made-inoperative-4218621%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fincome-tax-department-explains-why-pan-cards-of-some-nris-were-made-inoperative-4218621%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fincome-tax-department-explains-why-pan-cards-of-some-nris-were-made-inoperative-4218621%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20national%20held%20by%20N%20Korea%20after%20crossing%20border%20-%20UN%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689679130000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F83B3%2Fproduction%2F_115651733_breaking-large-promo-nc.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66233797%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20Nations%20command%20said%20the%20man%20was%20on%20an%20orientation%20tour%20when%20he%20crossed%20w