g%20against%20their%20continuous%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrouble%20erupted%20in%20the%20Hira%20Nagar%20sub-jail%2C%20which%20was%20notified%20as%20a%20holding%20centre%20in%20March%202020%2C%20when%20Rohingya%20refugees%20tried%20to%20step%20out%20of%20the%20jail%20in%20protest%20seeking%20their%20release.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20tried%20to%20break%20open%20the%20gate%20and%20come%20out%2C%20but%20we%20closed%20the%20gate%2C%E2%80%9D%20Superintendent%20of%20Kathua%20district%20jail%20and%20holding%20centre%20in-charge%2C%20Koushal%20Kumar%20told%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20a%20few%20persons%20also%20sustained%20minor%20injuries%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20tell%20you%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20persons%20injured.%20I%20myself%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20stone%20on%20the%20nose%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Rohingya%E2%80%99s%20pelted%20stones%20on%20the%20prison%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoushal%20said%20they%20have%20been%20frequently%20protesting%20in%20the%20detention%20centre%20to%20seek%20their%20repatriation%20to%20Myanmar.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20submitted%20their%20representations%20to%20the%20higher-ups%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20videos%20of%20the%20incident%20have%20also%20been%20shared%20in%20some%20WhatsApp%20groups.%20In%20one%20such%20video%2C%20a%20person%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20that%20teargas%20shells%20were%20fired%20upon%20them.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20eaten%20anything%20for%20the%20past%2027%20days.%20They%20fired%20teargas%20shells%20on%20us.%20Nobody%20has%20come%20to%20listen%20or%20see%20us.%20They%20also%20beat%20up%20women%20and%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20person%20can%20be%20heard%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20such%20video%2C%20a%20young%20person%20can%20be%20seen%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%20while%20men%20and%20women%20are%20returning%20presumably%20from%20the%20entrance%20gate%20of%20the%20detention%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20however%2C%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20independently%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20these%20video%20clips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20police%20reinforcements%20were%20rushed%20to%20the%20detention%20centre%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20this%20year%2C%20the%20refugees%20went%20on%20a%20protest%20and%20refused%20to%20eat%20on%20two%20occasions.%20They%20demanded%20that%20they%20either%20be%20deported%20to%20Myanmar%20or%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20from%20the%20civil%20administration%20and%20the%20prison%20department%20had%20then%20reached%20out%20to%20refugees%20and%20assured%20them%20that%20they%20would%20take%20up%20their%20demand%20with%20senior%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%E2%80%99s%20incident%20has%20left%20Rohingya%20families%20living%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Jammu%20worried%20about%20the%20well-being%20of%20their%20relatives%20lodged%20in%20the%20detention%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20go%20to%20Kathua%20jail%20but%20I%20am%20scared.%20My%20sister%20and%20brother-in-law%20have%20been%20there%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20I%20am%20worried%20about%20them%20after%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20teargas%20shells%20were%20lobbed%20in%20the%20detention%20centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ataullah%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%20Rohingya%20refugee%20living%20in%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20are%20facing%20worse%20treatment%20here%20than%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20our%20fault%20and%20crime%3F%20The%20authorities%20should%20tell%20us%20what%20wrong%20we%20have%20done%20or%20which%20law%20we%20have%20broken.%20We%20came%20here%20to%20save%20our%20lives%20but%20we%20had%20never%20thought%20that%20we%20would%20have%20to%20undergo%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20station%20house%20officer%2C%20Hira%20Nagar%20Police%20station%2C%20Amit%20Sangra%20said%20that%20they%20have%20registered%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetention%20of%20Rohingyas%20and%20rightwing%20campaigning%20for%20their%20ouster%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202021%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20authorities%20detained%20more%20than%20150%20Rohingya%20refugees%20living%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%20after%20the%20high%20court%20directed%20them%20to%20spell%20out%20what%20measures%20were%20being%20taken%20to%20identify%20and%20act%20on%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants.%E2%80%9D%20The%20court%20passed%20the%20direction%20responding%20to%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Hunar%20Gupta%2C%20who%20is%20affiliated%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20Gupta%20had%20approached%20the%20court%20seeking%20directions%20to%20the%20state%20government%20to%20shift%20all%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20from%20Myanmar%20and%20Bangladesh%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20to%20any%20other%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20petition%20also%20sought%20necessary%20directions%20to%20a%20former%20retired%20judge%20to%20hold%20an%20inquiry%20to%20identify%20all%20the%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20from%20Myanmar%20and%20Bangladesh%20living%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rightwing%20groups%20in%20Jammu%20have%20been%20campaigning%20for%20the%20ouster%20of%20Rohingyas%20from%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20are%20Rohingya%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohingya%20are%20a%20Muslim%20ethnic%20minority%20group%20who%20have%20lived%20for%20centuries%20in%20a%20predominantly%20Buddhist%20Myanmar%20%E2%80%93%20formerly%20known%20as%20Burma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohingya%20have%20suffered%20decades%20of%20violence%2C%20discrimination%20and%20persecution%20in%20Myanmar%20and%20have%20been%20denied%20citizenship%20since%201982.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20Rohingya%20have%20fled%20to%20different%20countries%20to%20escape%20persecution%