n%3Cli%3EStocks%20appear%20fairly%20valued%20after%20their%20stellar%20first-half%20rally%2C%20limiting%20further%20upside%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EConquering%20inflation%20won't%20be%20easy%2C%20a%20US%20recession%20could%20still%20strike%2C%20and%20stocks%20could%20disappoint%20bulls%20in%20the%20second%20half%2C%20Aswath%20Damodaran%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20professor%20at%20NYU%20Stern%2C%20whose%20nickname%20is%20the%20%26quot%3BDean%20of%20Valuation%2C%26quot%3B%20shared%20his%20outlook%20for%20markets%20and%20the%20economy%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faswathdamodaran.blogspot.com%2F2023%2F07%2Fmarket-resilience-or-investors-in.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emid-year%20assessment%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20Monday.%20He%20cautioned%20that%20even%20though%20inflation%20has%20slowed%20from%20a%2040-year%20high%20of%209.1%25%20to%20only%203%25%20in%20June%2C%20it%20still%20remains%20above%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%202%25%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20last%20stretch%20getting%20inflation%20down%20from%203%25%20to%20below%202%25%20will%20be%20trench%20warfare%2C%20and%20we%20will%20be%20exposed%20to%20macro%20shocks%20(from%20energy%20prices%20or%20regional%20unrest)%20that%20can%20create%20inflationary%20shocks%2C%26quot%3B%20Damodaran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20poured%20cold%20water%20on%20hopes%20that%20now%20inflation%20is%20fading%2C%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20will%20cut%20interest%20rates%20and%20the%20economy%20will%20escape%20a%20downturn.%20The%20US%20central%20bank%20hiked%20its%20benchmark%20rate%20from%20almost%20zero%20to%20north%20of%205%25%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months%20in%20order%20to%20curb%20price%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20signs%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20cooling%20and%20it%20is%20again%20entirely%20possible%20that%20this%20turns%20into%20a%20slow-motion%20recession%2C%20as%20real%20estate%20(espec