llegedly%20incapacitating%20six%20police%20personnel%20who%20were%20accompanying%20them%20to%20a%20court%20hearing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFootage%20of%20the%20daring%20murder%20shows%20the%20eight%20assailants%20spending%20nearly%20two%20minutes%20in%20the%20bus%20and%20stepping%20out%20several%20times%20to%20reload%20their%20weapons%2C%20even%20as%20terrified%20passengers%20exit%20the%20vehicle%20by%20climbing%20out%20of%20the%20windows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20took%20place%20on%20July%2012%2C%20when%20gangster%20Kuldeep%20Jagheena%20and%20his%20accomplice%20Vijaypal%20were%20being%20taken%20for%20a%20hearing%20at%20a%20court%20in%20Bharatpur%20from%20the%20Jaipur%20Central%20Jail.%20The%20men%2C%20both%20accused%20of%20murder%2C%20were%20travelling%20in%20a%20Rajasthan%20Roadways%20bus%20and%20were%20accompanied%20by%20six%20police%20personnel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20which%20has%20emerged%20today%2C%20shows%20the%20bus%20standing%20at%20Amoli%20toll%20plaza%20in%20Bharatpur%20when%20it%20is%20approached%20by%20three%20men%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20flaunting%20a%20gun.%20They%20are%20seen%20waiting%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20near%20the%20door%20of%20the%20bus%2C%20until%20a%20shot%20is%20fired%2C%20sending%20a%20few%20passengers%20scurrying%20to%20safety.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20men%20then%20approach%20the%20door%20of%20the%20bus%20and%20begin%20firing%20as%20a%20third%20peers%20in%20through%20the%20windows%2C%20presumably%20looking%20for%20the%20targets.%20One%20of%20the%20men%20enters%20the%20bus%20and%20opens%20fire%2C%20before%20calmly%20exiting%20and%20then%20pushing%20three%20other%20shooters%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20other%20passengers%20exit%20the%20bus%20through%20the%20door%20and%20some%20clamber%20out%20of%20the%20windows.%20More%20shooters%20approach%20the%20bus%20and%20the%20men%20then%20take%20turns%20exiting%20the%20vehicle%20to%20reload%20after%20running%20out%20of%20