ies%20to%20the%20US%20in%202019%2C%20on%20the%20condition%20they%20be%20returned%20within%20weeks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20almost%20four%20years%20later%2C%20they're%20%26quot%3Bstuck%26quot%3B%20at%20Donald%20Trump's%20Mar-a-Lago%20residence%2C%20per%20Haaretz.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESenior%20Israeli%20figures%20have%20tried%20but%20failed%20to%20get%20the%20antiquities%20back%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Israel%20sent%20some%20of%20its%20national%20treasures%20for%20an%20event%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20they%20be%20returned%20within%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20almost%20four%20years%20later%2C%20the%20ancient%20artifacts%20are%20%26quot%3Bstuck%26quot%3B%20at%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20Mar-a-Lago%20resort%20in%20Florida%2C%20with%20senior%20Israeli%20figures%20scrambling%20to%20get%20them%20back%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com.%2Fisrael-news%2F2023-07-18%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fisraeli-antiquities-remain-stranded-at-trumps-estate-as-authorities-fail-to-retrieve%2F00000189-6448-dc6b-a3f9-ee593e850000%3Futm_source%3Dflipboard%26utm_content%3Dtopic%252Fmiddleeast%5C%22%3Eper%20the%20Israeli%20newspaper%20Haaretz.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20artifacts%20include%20ancient%20ceramic%20candles%2C%20which%20were%20sent%20from%20Israel%20to%20the%20US%20for%20a%20Hanukkah%20event%20at%20the%20White%20House%20attended%20by%20Trump%2C%20who%20was%20then%20president%2C%20Haaretz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20candles%20were%20meant%20to%20be%20displayed%20briefly%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20be%20exhibited%20due%20to%20an%20unspecified%20bureaucratic%20issue%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20being%20returned%20to%20Israel%2C%20however%2C%20they%20remained%20in%20the%20US%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20according%20to%20Haaretz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Hasson%2C%20who%20was%20the%20d