jpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20picture%20taken%20on%20July%2017%2C%202023%20shows%20a%20Russian%20warship%20sailing%20near%20the%20Kerch%20bridge%2C%20linking%20the%20Russian%20mainland%20to%20Crimea%2C%20following%20an%20attack%20claimed%20by%20Ukrainian%20forces.%3Cp%3ESTRINGER%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERussian%20tourists%20are%20snarling%20up%20military%20supply%20routes%20near%20Crimea%2C%20a%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDespite%20it%20being%20a%20war%20zone%2C%20tourists%20are%20still%20visiting%20the%20occupied%20Crimean%20peninsula.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20Ukrainian%20attack%20on%20a%20major%20bridge%20prompted%20many%20to%20flee%2C%20reports%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20tourists%20are%20snarling%20up%20crucial%20military%20supply%20routes%20as%20the%20Kremlin%20continues%20to%20encourage%20civilians%20to%20visit%20the%20occupied%20Crimea%20peninsula%20despite%20it%20being%20a%20war%20zone%2C%20a%20report%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20traffic%20jams%20caused%20by%20tourists%20were%20made%20worse%20this%20week%20after%20an%20explosion%20tore%20through%20the%20Kerch%20road%20bridge%20on%20Sunday%2C%20with%20Russia%20blaming%20the%20attack%20on%20drones%20launched%20by%20Ukraine.%20Ukraine%20Monday%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20forced%20the%20temporary%20closure%20of%20the%20bridge%20for%20a%20second%20time%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-july-17-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%20described%20the%20Kerch%20bridge%20as%20one%20of%20two%20supply%20routes%20for%20Russian%20forces%20in%20southern%20Ukraine%20battling%20to%20resist%20a%20Ukrainian%20counteroffensive.%20The%20other%20route%20runs%20through%20Russian-occupied%20regions%20in%20east%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20July%2017%20attack%20on%20the%20Kerch%20Strait%20Bridge%20will%20likely%20have%20continuing%20ramifications%20on%20Russian%20logistics%20in%20southern%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussian%20and%20occupation%20officials%20have%20nevertheless%20continued%20to%20promote%20occupied%20Crimea%20as%20a%20tourist%20destination%2C%20however%2C%20urging%20Russian%20civilians%20to%20drive%20through%20and%20to%20a%20warzone%20rather%20than%20advising%20them%20to%20avoid%20it%20as%20a%20responsible%20government%20would%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22887%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20tourists%20in%20Crimea%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b6617adb902600193564b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22665%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20tourists%20in%20the%20resort%20town%20of%20Alushta%20on%20the%20Crimean%20peninsula%20on%20June%2018%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EOLGA%20MALTSEVA%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kerch%20bridge%20is%20one%20of%20Putin's%20most%20prized%20projects%2C%20and%20was%20built%20after%20Russia%20occupied%20the%20Crimean%20peninsula%20in%202014.%20It%20spans%20the%2012-mile%20Kerch%20strait%2C%20connecting%20Crimea%20with%20southern%20Russia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20Russian%20occupation%20authorities%20had%20already%20been%20struggling%20to%20cope%20with%20traffic%20issues%20on%20the%20bridge.%20Despite%20this%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20had%20ordered%20Russian%20military%20vehicles%20to%20help%20ferry%20tourists%20to%20the%20location%2C%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20Sunday's%20attack%2C%20in%20which%20Russian%20officials%20said%20two%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20Russian%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fria.ru%2F20230717%2Fmost-1884707249.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estate%20media%20reported%20%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0traffic%20jams%20reportedly%20stretching%20for%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20was%20the%20second%20on%20the%20bridge%20in%20a%20year%2C%20with%20Ukraine%20blowing%20up%20the%20railway%20section%20of%20the%20bridge%20in%20October%202022.%20Ukraine%20has%20also%20targeted%20several%20military%20sites%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Russian%20government's%20continued%20failure%20to%20put%20Russian%20society%20on%20a%20war-time%20footing%20will%20have%20significant%20impacts%20on%20Russian%20logistics%20as%20traffic%20from%20Russian%20tourism%20to%20occupied%20Crimea%20jams%20Russian%20logistics%20to%20southern%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Ukrainian%20counteroffensive%20in%20the%20south%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Russian%20authorities%20seeking%20to%20encourage%20holidaymakers%20to%20visit%20Crimea%2C%20whose%20economy%20is%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20tourism%2C%20the%20number%20of%20visitors%20fell%20by%20a%20third%20last%20year%2C%20when%20Russia%20launched%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20has%20fallen%20again%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.themoscowtimes.com%2F2023%2F06%2F16%2Fcrimeas-tourism-industry-faces-another-lost-summer-as-war-rages-on-a81541%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Moscow%20Times%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20Sunday's%20attack%2C%20Putin%20urged%20tourists%20to%20avoid%20the%20Kerch%20bridge%20and%20instead%20take%20the%20route%20through%20occupied%20east%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20yesterday%20I%20was%20thinking%20what%20a%20moron%20one%20should%20be%20to%20go%20on%20holiday%20to%20Crimea%20now.%20Well%2C%20now%20the%20holiday%20will%20definitely%20be%20remembered%20when%20they%20go%20home%20through%20the%20front%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20Russian%20quipped%20on%20Telegram%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailybeast.com%2Fdrone-strike-on-crimea-bridge-sparks-mass-exodus-of-russian-tourists%3Fref%3Dtopic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Daily%20Beast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-military-supply-routes-blocked-tourists-crimea-putin-bridge-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689676167000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b65f31db9026001935645c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-military-supply-routes-blocked-tourists-crimea-putin-bridge-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russian%20state%20media%20broadcast%20traffic%20jams%20as%20tourists%20tried%20to%20drive%20home%20through%20southern%20Ukraine%20after%20a%20blast%20on%20the%20Kerch%20bridge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tporter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Porter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-military-supply-routes-blocked-tourists-crimea-putin-bridge-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Analysis%3A%20Challenges%20For%20%5C%22Bigger%5C%22%20NDA%20Ahead%20Of%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20holds%20its%20big%20show%20of%20strength%20today%2C%20ground%20realities%20indicate%20that%20an%20understanding%20with%20each%20ally%20will%20be%20no%20cakewalk.%20The%2024-party%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee-led%20NDA%20has%20grown%20into%20a%2038-party%20coalition%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Seat-sharing%20negotiations%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20tough%2C%20especially%20in%20states%20like%20Bihar%20and%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBihar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20contested%20the%20national%20election%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%20and%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan's%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP).%20The%20BJP%20and%20JDU%20contested%2017%20seats%20each%20in%20Bihar%20and%20the%20LJP%20got%20six%20seats.%20The%20LJP%20was%20also%20given%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20which%20became%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan's%20route%20to%20parliament.%20The%20NDA%20won%2039%20of%20Bihar's%2040%20seats%3B%20the%20BJP%20won%2017%20seats%2C%20JDU%2016%20and%20the%20LJP%20won%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20has%20changed%20since%20then.%20The%20JDU%20has%20switched%20sides%2C%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20forming%20a%20new%20government%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20and%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20after%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan's%20death%20in%202020%2C%20the%20LJP%20split%2C%20and%20his%20son%20Chirag%20Paswan%20was%20isolated%20by%20a%20faction%20of%20MPs%20led%20by%20his%20uncle%20Pashupati%20Paras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20now%20wants%20both%20factions%20to%20merge%2C%20but%20Pashupati%20Paras%20is%20unwilling%20to%20reunite%20with%20his%20nephew.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20has%20said%20he%20expects%20the%20same%20deal%20for%20his%20party%20as%20in%202019%20-%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%20one%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20resolve%20this%20will%20be%20a%20big%20challenge%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20since%20other%20regional%20players%20like%20Upendra%20Kushwaha%20and%20Jitan%20Ram%20Majhi%20will%20expect%20a%20good%20share%20in%20seats.%20The%20BJP%20would%20want%20to%20contest%20the%20maximum%20seats%20possible%20as%20this%20time%2C%20there%20is%20no%20JDU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaharashtra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20were%20together%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Of%20the%20state's%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20contested%2025%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%2023%20seats.%20The%20BJP%20won%2023%20seats%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20year%2C%20after%20the%20Maharashtra%20election%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20broke%20off%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20formed%20a%20coalition%20government%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20government%20crashed%20after%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20split%20last%20year%2C%20and%20a%20faction%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20has%20asked%20for%20all%2018%20seats%20that%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20had%20contested%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20has%20also%20split%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20has%20joined%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-BJP%20coalition.%20The%20NCP%20had%20won%20four%20seats%20in%202019.%20Dividing%20up%20Maharashtra's%2048%20seats%20with%20its%20allies%20will%20be%20a%20difficult%20prospect%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20contested%20the%20polls%20with%20Apna%20Dal%2C%20which%20won%20both%20the%20seats%20it%20was%20allocated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20OP%20Rajbhar's%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20the%20Nishad%20Party%20have%20joined%20the%20NDA.%20There%20is%20a%20buzz%20about%20them%20joining%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath-led%20BJP%20government%20in%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20also%20in%20talks%20with%20Jayant%20Chowdhary%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD).%20The%20party%20has%20reportedly%20asked%20Mr%20Chowdhary%20to%20merge%20his%20party%20with%20it%2C%20but%20he%20is%20reluctant%20to%20do%20so.%20If%20the%20RLD%20does%20join%20the%20NDA%2C%20then%20it%20will%20also%20expect%20a%20share%20of%20seats%20to%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20a%20tie-up%20with%20the%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20smaller%20regional%20parties.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20had%20contested%2020%20of%20the%20state's%2030%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20PMK%20seven%2C%20BJP%20five%2C%20DMDK%20four%2C%20Tamil%20Manila%20Congress%20one%2C%20Puthiya%20Tamilagam%20one%20and%20PNK%20one%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20more%20new%20parties%20are%20likely%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20focusing%20specially%20on%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20There%20is%20also%20speculation%20about%20PM%20Modi%20contesting%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20after%20his%20outreach%20to%20the%20state%20in%20multiple%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaryana%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20Dushyant%20Chautala's%20Jananayak%20Janata%20Party%20(JJP)%20are%20running%20a%20coalition%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20plans%20to%20contest%20all%2010%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20and%20will%20not%20attempt%20any%20pact%20with%20the%20JJP.%20There%20are%20reports%20that%20the%20two%20parties%20may%20break%20up%20before%20the%202024%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJharkhand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20contested%20the%202019%20election%20with%20the%20All%20Jharkhand%20Students'%20Union%20(AJSU).%20The%20BJP%20won%2011%20of%20the%20state's%2014%20seats%20and%20AJSU%20took%20one.%20The%20two%20may%20fight%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20together%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAssam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20contested%20the%20election%20with%20Asom%20Gana%20Parishad%20(AGP)%20and%20Bodoland%20People's%20Front%20(BPF).%20The%20BJP%20contested%2010%20of%20the%20state's%2014%20seats%20and%20won%20nine.%20The%20AGP%20contested%20three%20and%20the%20BPF%20one%2C%20but%20both%20scored%20ducks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20regions%2C%20like%20Kerala%20and%20northeast%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20on%20relatively%20firmer%20ground%20as%20its%20allies%20have%20limited%20strength%20and%20do%20not%20enjoy%20much%20bargaining%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689676080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F0dh4nq9o_modi-shah-nadda_625x300_06_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-challenges-for-bigger-nda-ahead-of-2024-4218335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20holds%20its%20big%20show%20of%20strength%20today%2C%20ground%20realities%20indicate%20that%20an%20understanding%20with%20each%20ally%20will%20be%20no%20cakewalk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-challenges-for-bigger-nda-ahead-of-2024-4218335%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-challenges-for-bigger-nda-ahead-of-2024-4218335%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-challenges-for-bigger-nda-ahead-of-2024-4218335%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20get%20a%20VIP%2F%20fancy%20registration%20number%20for%20your%20car%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689676022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101858521%2Cimgsize-40256.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fadvice-centre%2Fhow-to-get-a-vip%2F-fancy-registration-number-for-your-car-step-by-step-guide%2Farticleshow%2F101858017.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you%E2%80%99re%20planning%20to%20purchase%20a%20car%20and%20have%20a%20fancy%2FVIP%20number%20on%20your%20bucket%20list%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20a%20step-by-step%20guide%20on%20how%20to%20get%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fadvice-centre%2Fhow-to-get-a-vip%2F-fancy-registration-number-for-your-car-step-by-step-guide%2Farticleshow%2F101858017.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opposition%20Parties'%20Front%20Has%20a%20New%20Name%3A%20'INDIA'%2C%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18155503%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-18-at-1.20.10-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengaluru%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20opposition%20front%20comprising%2026%20parties%20has%20a%20new%20name%3A%20INDIA%2C%20which%20stands%20for%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance.%20All%2026%20parties%20have%20mutually%20agreed%20to%20this%20new%20name%20for%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20opposition%20fronts%20since%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20was%20agreed%20upon%20at%20the%20opposition%20parties%E2%80%99%20second%20meeting%20held%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20July%2018.%20The%20first%20meeting%20was%20held%20in%20Patna%20on%20June%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20there%20were%20some%20reservations%20regarding%20having%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98alliance%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20new%20name%2C%20given%20the%20uncertainty%20over%20seat%20sharing%20in%20a%20few%20states%2C%20but%20eventually%20agreed%20to%20the%20term%20to%20send%20a%20message%20that%20all%20the%20parties%20have%20common%20ideological%20concerns%20against%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%2C%20opposition%20leaders%20believe%2C%20will%20assert%20the%20front%E2%80%99s%20conviction%20to%20%E2%80%9Csafeguard%20democracy%2C%20constitution%2C%20and%20diversity%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20the%20stated%20goal%20of%20the%20opposition%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20convincing%20the%20few%20parties%20which%20had%20some%20reservations%20about%20the%20name%20to%20come%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20am%20happy%20that%2026%20parties%20are%20present%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20work%20unitedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20we%20are%20in%20government%20in%2011%20states%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20did%20not%20get%20303%20seats%20by%20itself.%20It%20used%20the%20votes%20of%20its%20allies%20and%20came%20to%20power%20and%20then%20discarded%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20President%20and%20their%20leaders%20are%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLyEkcmQi82%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FLyEkcmQi82%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1681217796762484736%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tweet%2C%20Kharge%20indicated%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20differences%20were%20largely%20ironed%20out%20during%20the%20opposition%20summit%20in%20Bengaluru.%20He%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20parallel%20NDA%20meeting%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20said%20that%20the%20opposition%20resolve%20to%20unitedly%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%202024%20has%20forced%20the%20BJP%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpatch%20up%E2%80%9D%20with%20its%20older%20allies%20that%20it%20had%20deserted%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20press%20after%20the%20four-hour%20long%20meeting%2C%20Kharge%20who%20also%20chaired%20the%20discussions%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20said%20that%20the%20name%20for%20the%20opposition%20front%20was%20agreed%20upon%20by%20every%20party%20unanimously%20after%20discussions%20and%20reflects%20the%20larger%20philosophy%20behind%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccoming%20together%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20very%20important%20meeting%20to%20save%20democracy%20and%20our%20Constitution.%20We%20have%20all%20come%20together%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20Indian%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20while%20elaborating%20on%20how%20diverse%20political%20parties%2C%20despite%20their%20differences%2C%20have%20joined%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20the%20leaders%20were%20present%20at%20the%20stage%2C%20barring%20the%20Bihar%20and%20Kashmir%20leaders%20like%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20and%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20who%20rushed%20to%20catch%20their%20flights%20soon%20after%20the%20meeting%20got%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20also%20said%20that%20while%20a%20name%20for%20the%20alliance%20was%20decided%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20third%20such%20meeting%20of%20the%2026%20parties%20will%20soon%20take%20place%20in%20Mumbai%20where%20remaining%20details%20will%20be%20finalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%2011-member%20coordination%20committee%20will%20be%20set%20up%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%A6A%20central%20secretariat%20will%20also%20be%20set%20up%20for%20campaign%20management%20and%20joint%20rallies%20and%20action%20there.%20The%20secretariat%20will%20work%20out%20of%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2011-member%20coordination%20committee%20will%20be%20representative%20of%20all%20parties%20and%20will%20decide%20the%20future%20course%20of%20electoral%20and%20political%20strategy%20including%20communication%20points%2C%20joint%20rallies%2C%20seat-sharing%20and%20other%20such%20aspects%20of%20the%20opposition%20front.%20Kharge%20added%20that%20the%20front%20will%20choose%20its%20president%20and%20convenor%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20that%20the%20leaders%20have%20not%20come%20together%20for%20power%20or%20to%20%E2%80%9Cattain%20something%E2%80%9D%20but%20to%20%E2%80%9Csave%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20leaders%20have%20shown%20that%20they%20can%20come%20together%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20Indian%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20front%20also%20adopted%20a%20joint%20resolution%20that%20deftly%20accommodates%20the%20political%20agendas%20of%20different%20participants.%20It%20raises%20concerns%20over%20alleged%20attacks%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20federal%20structure%2C%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20failures%20on%20the%20economic%20front%2C%20and%20misuse%20of%20gubernatorial%20offices%20and%20central%20investigation%20agencies%20%E2%80%93%20a%20criticism%20that%20parties%20like%20the%20Congress%2C%20DMK%2C%20TMC%20and%20AAP%20have%20constantly%20been%20raising.%20It%20hits%20out%20on%20the%20increasing%20attacks%20on%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%20and%20working%20classes%2C%20farmers%20and%20farm%20labourers%20%E2%80%93%20a%20point%20that%20is%20integral%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20parties%20like%20VCK%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20and%20Left%20parties%20that%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20resolution%20pledged%20to%20advocate%20for%20a%20pan-Indian%20caste%20census%20that%20has%20been%20raised%20by%20socialist%20parties%20like%20SP%2C%20RJD%20and%20JD(U).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20the%20resolution%20has%20accommodated%20varied%20political%20interests%20of%20both%20national%20and%20regional%20parties%20is%20reflective%20of%20the%20unprecedented%20unity%20that%20the%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20been%20traditional%20rivals%2C%20have%20achieved%20in%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20also%20shows%20the%20flexibility%20and%20resolve%20that%20each%20opposition%20party%20has%20shown%20in%20trying%20to%20forge%20a%20united%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20other%20four%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20who%20spoke%20after%20Kharge%20highlighted%20that%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20fight%20against%20BJP%20will%20be%20along%20ideological%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20taken%20up%20this%20challenge.%20BJP%2C%20can%20you%20challenge%20INDIA%3F%E2%80%9D%20Banerjee%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20and%20Thackeray%20spoke%20about%20how%20INDIA%20will%20be%20a%20joint%20challenge%20of%20democratic%20people%20to%20the%20authoritarian%20ways%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20Kejriwal%20said%20that%20the%20front%20will%20highlight%20how%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20snatched%20away%20people%E2%80%99s%20resources%20to%20distribute%20it%20among%20a%20few%20rich%20people%2C%20even%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20failed%20to%20deliver%20on%20every%20front%20over%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20exhorted%20people%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20to%20fear%E2%80%9D%20the%20Modi%20government%20anymore.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20here.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20fear%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20asserted%3A%20%E2%80%9COur%20fight%20is%20against%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ideology%20and%20its%20thinking.%20We%20have%20named%20our%20front%20INDIA%20because%20our%20India%20is%20under%20attack%20and%20we%20realised%20that%20the%20fight%20is%20not%20between%20two%20political%20formations.%20The%20fight%20is%20between%20two%20different%20ideas%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689676012000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18155503%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-18-at-1.20.10-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fopposition-parties-front-has-a-new-name-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20also%20said%20that%20while%20a%20name%20for%20the%20alliance%20was%20decided%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20third%20such%20meeting%20of%20the%2026%20parties%20will%20soon%20take%20place%20in%20Mumbai%20where%20remaining%20details%20will%20be%20finalised.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fopposition-parties-front-has-a-new-name-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20top%20AI%20expert%20says%20most%20outsourced%20coders%20in%20India%20will%20be%20out%20of%20a%20job%20in%202%20years%20thanks%20to%20the%20technology%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emad%20Mostaque%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Stability%20AI%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F642db191de7d9200193a277a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20top%20AI%20expert%20says%20that%20most%20outsourced%20coders%20in%20India%20will%20be%20gone%20in%202%20years%3Cp%3EStability%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStability%20AI%20CEO%20Emad%20Mostaque%20thinks%20AI%20will%20eliminate%20most%20outsourced%20coding%20jobs%20in%20India.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20he%20made%20such%20a%20bold%20call.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DciX_iFGyS0M%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20said%20AI%20would%20make%20most%20programmers%20obsolete%20in%205%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20will%20soon%20eliminate%20most%20outsourced%20coding%20jobs%20in%20India%20as%20the%20technology%20will%20drastically%20reduce%20the%20need%20for%20them%2C%20according%20to%20a%20leading%20AI%20expert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia's%20%26quot%3Boutsourced%20coders%20up%20to%20level%20three%20programmers%20will%20be%20gone%20in%20the%20next%20year%20or%20two%2C%20whereas%20in%20France%2C%20you'll%20never%20fire%20a%20developer%2C%26quot%3B%20Emad