%20pm%20in%20the%20same%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20questioned%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20bail%20for%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20to%20which%20they%20said%20the%20accused%20is%20not%20meeting%20any%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20Tomar%2C%20the%20suspended%20assistant%20secretary%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%2C%20was%20also%20granted%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20had%20to%20furnish%20a%20personal%20bond%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20accused%20appeared%20before%20the%20court%20in%20pursuance%20of%20summons%20issued%20to%20them%2C%20and%20sought%20bail%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20wrestlers%20have%20questioned%20the%20intent%20of%20the%20oversight%20panel%20that%20probed%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20accusations%20against%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20and%20alleged%20that%20it%20was%20biased%20towards%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government-formed%20six-member%20panel%2C%20led%20by%20the%20legendary%20Indian%20boxer%20MC%20Mary%20Kom%2C%20had%20submitted%20its%20report%20to%20the%20government%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20has%20refused%20to%20step%20down%20despite%20the%20charge%20sheet%20filed%20against%20him%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20filed%20a%201000-page%20charge%20sheet%20against%20the%20Federation%20chief%20after%20a%20detailed%20investigation%20that%20included%20questioning%20over%20100%20people.%2015%20of%20those%20questioned%20testified%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20seven%20wrestlers%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%20Among%20them%20were%20the%20wrestlers'%20friends%20and%20families.%20%26quot%3BThe%20evidence%20is%20enough%20to%20try%20and%20punish%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faccused-of-molestation-stalking-wrestling-chief-says-wont-step-down-4198359%5C%22%3Epolice%20sources%20have%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20had%20filed%20a%20charge%20sheet%20against%20the%20six-time%20MP%20on%20June%2015%20under%20sections%20354%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20a%20woman%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty)%2C%20354A%20(sexual%20harassment)%2C%20354D%20(stalking)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tomar%20was%20charged%20with%20offences%20under%20IPC%20sections%20109%20(abetment%20of%20any%20offence%2C%20if%20the%20act%20abetted%20is%20committed%20in%20consequence%2C%20and%20where%20no%20express%20provision%20is%20made%20for%20its%20punishment)%2C%20354%2C%20354A%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh's%20counsel%20alleged%20media%20trail%2C%20to%20which%20the%20judge%20said%20he%20may%20move%20an%20application%20before%20the%20high%20court%20or%20trial%20court.%20The%20court%20will%20pass%20an%20appropriate%20order%20on%20the%20application%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20move%20any%20application%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20present%20case%2C%20another%20FIR%20was%20registered%20against%20Mr%20Singh%20pursuant%20to%20allegations%20made%20by%20a%20minor%20wrestler%2C%20which%20was%20registered%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act.%20She%20was%20among%20the%20seven%20female%20grapplers%20who%20had%20accused%20Mr%20Singh%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20police%2C%20though%2C%20have%20requested%20a%20cancellation%20of%20the%20POCSO%20case%2C%20citing%20lack%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20FIRs%20mentioned%20several%20alleged%20instances%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20like%20inappropriate%20touching%2C%20groping%2C%20stalking%20and%20intimidation%20by%20M