2Fphoto%2F101857987.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBhumi%20Pednekar%20believes%20that%20there's%20a%20lot%20more%20to%20her%20than%20her%20'film%20image'%20and%20hence%20loves%20to%20explore%20that%20side%20on%20social%20media.%20She's%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20this%20fashionista%20who's%20quite%20confident%20about%20her%20choices.%20Bhumi%20reveals%20what%20changed%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20She%20also%20speaks%20about%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20women%20in%20every%20field.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Ankita%20Kanabar%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbhumi-pednekar-on-the-evolution-of-her-fashion-pay-disparity-sexism-and-the-lady-killer-with-arjun-kapoor-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F101857987.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Portal%20Launched%20To%20Help%2010%20Crore%20Sahara%20Depositors%20Get%20Refund%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%20was%20launched%20today%2C%20bringing%20much-awaited%20relief%20to%20as%20many%20as%2010%20crore%20people.%20The%20portal%20will%20facilitate%20the%20process%20of%20refunding%20the%20money%20that%20depositors%20put%20in%20four%20cooperative%20societies%20of%20Sahara%20Group%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20process%20of%20returning%20the%20money%20of%20depositors%2C%20which%20was%20stuck%20in%20four%20cooperative%20societies%20of%20Sahara%20Group%2C%20has%20started%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20while%20launching%20the%20refund%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20said%20that%20initially%20Rs%2010%2C000%20will%20be%20returned%20to%20investors%20on%20a%20trial%20basis.%20Gradually%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20refund%20may%20be%20increased%20if%20the%20trial%20succeeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%201.7%20crore%20investors%20can%20register%20on%20the%20refund%20portal%20and%20claim%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20in%20the%20first%20phase.%20According%20to%20Mr%20Shah%2C%20there%20are%204%20crore%20depositors%20who%20are%20eligible%20to%20get%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20assured%20Sahara%20depositors%20that%20their%20money%20is%20safe%20and%20that%20they%20will%20receive%20a%20refund%20within%2045%20days%20of%20registering%20on%20the%20CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20the%20portal%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%20will%20work%20by%20linking%20your%20Aadhaar%20number%20to%20your%20mobile%20phone%20number%20and%20bank%20account.%20You%20will%20also%20need%20to%20provide%20receipt%20details.%20Once%20you%20have%20done%20this%2C%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20download%20a%20form%2C%20fill%20it%20out%2C%20and%20re-upload%20it%20to%20the%20portal.%20The%20refund%20process%20will%20then%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20will%20it%20take%20to%20get%20a%20refund%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20the%20money%20will%20be%20deposited%20into%20the%20bank%20account%20of%20the%20claimant%20within%2045%20days.%20The%20Home%20Minister%20urged%20to%20use%20the%20Common%20Services%20Centers%20(CSC)%20digital%20services%20in%20case%20of%20any%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20will%20CRCS%20Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20the%20CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%20is%20to%20protect%20the%20interests%20of%20members%20of%20the%20cooperatives.%20The%20portal%20will%20help%20address%20the%20genuine%20claims%20of%20depositors%20who%20had%20invested%20money%20in%20Sahara%20Group's%20cooperative%20societies%20namely%20-%20Sahara%20Credit%20Cooperative%20Society%20Ltd%2C%20Saharayan%20Universal%20Multipurpose%20Society%20Ltd%2C%20Humara%20India%20Credit%20Cooperative%20Society%20Ltd%20and%20Stars%20Multipurpose%20Cooperative%20Society%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20dated%2029th%20March%202023%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20that%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20be%20transferred%20out%20of%20the%20'Sahara-SEBI%20Refund%20Account'%20to%20the%20Central%20Registrar%20of%20Cooperative%20Societies%20(CRCS)%20for%20disbursement%20against%20the%20legitimate%20dues%20of%20the%20genuine%20depositors%20of%20Sahara%20Group%20of%20Cooperative%20Societies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689675060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fijsje7l_sahara-chief-subrata-roy-650_625x300_31_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fportal-launched-to-help-10-crore-sahara-depositors-get-refund-4218267%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CRCS-Sahara%20Refund%20Portal%20was%20launched%20today%2C%20bringing%20much-awaited%20relief%20to%20as%20many%20as%2010%20crore%20people.%20The%20portal%20will%20facilitate%20the%20process%20of%20refunding%20the%20money%20that%20depositors%20put%20in%20four%20cooperative%20societies%20of%20Sahara%20Group%2C%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fportal-launched-to-help-10-crore-sahara-depositors-get-refund-4218267%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fportal-launched-to-help-10-crore-sahara-depositors-get-refund-4218267%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fportal-launched-to-help-10-crore-sahara-depositors-get-refund-4218267%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Jumps%20In%20Front%20Of%20Moving%20Bus%20Hoping%20Compensation%20Would%20Help%20Children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20in%20Salem%20has%20died%20by%20suicide%20after%20throwing%20herself%20in%20front%20of%20a%20moving%20bus%2C%20ho