6%20and%20set%20July%2028%20as%20the%20next%20date%20of%20hearing.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Tripura%20state%20wing%20of%20the%20WFI%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwrestling-federation-of-india-elections-face-further-delay%5C%22%3Epetitioned%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20high%20court%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20electoral%20college%2C%20leading%20to%20concerns%20over%20further%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20still%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20elections%20can%20be%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federation%20is%20facing%20elections%20after%20a%2040-day%20protest%20at%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jantar%20Mantar%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20wrestlers%20against%20the%20lack%20of%20police%20action%20on%20serious%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20its%20chief%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20sports%20minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20had%20promised%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers%20that%20fresh%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20to%20select%20leadership%20for%20the%20federation%2C%20which%20Brij%20Bhushan%20headed%20for%2012%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20of%20rampant%20wrongdoing%20surround%20Brij%20Bhushan%20and%20his%20assistant%20secretary%20Vinod%20Tomar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bhushan%20is%20supposed%20to%20appear%20before%20a%20trial%20court%20today%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20World%20Wrestling%20(UWW)%2C%20the%20international%20governing%20body%20for%20amateur%20wrestling%2C%20had%20earlier%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F655711%2Fuww-protesting-wrestlers-statement%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20failure%20to%20uphold%20the%20deadline%20for%20election%20to%20the%20WFI%20%E2%80%9Cmay%20lead%20UWW%20to%20suspend%20the%20federation%2C%20thereby%20forcing%20the%20athletes%20to%20compete%20under%20a%20neutral%20flag.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Finternational-olympic-committee-asks-indian-olympic-body-to-address-issues-including-wrestlers%5C%22%3Easked%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20to%20%E2%80%9Caddress%20a%20number%20of%20ongoing%20issues%20affecting%20Indian%20Sports%20Federations%2C%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20coordinated%20manner%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20rules%20and%20directives%20of%20the%20International%20Federations%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20then%20stressed%20that%20this%20%E2%80%9Cincludes%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20the%20situation%20of%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689674449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F20172512%2F2022_5img20_May_2022_PTI05_20_2022_000129B-min.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-removes-gauhati-hcs-stay-of-wrestling-federation-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20federation%20is%20facing%20elections%20after%20an%20almost%2040-day%20protest%20at%20New%20Delhi%20by%20India's%20top%20wrestlers%20against%20the%20lack%20of%20police%20action%20on%20serious%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20its%20chief%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-removes-gauhati-hcs-stay-of-wrestling-federation-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDA's%2038%20vs%20oppn's%2026%3A%20List%20of%20parties%20attending%20rival%20meetings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689673900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fthumb%2Fmsid-101857303%2Cwidth-1070%2Cheight-580%2Cimgsize-79946%2Cresizemode-75%2Coverlay-toi_sw%2Cpt-32%2Cy_pad-40%2Fphoto.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2