y%20of%20norms%20and%20lack%20of%20legislations%20for%20gender%20equality%20in%20an%20intimate%20relationship%20can%20have%20material%20(and%20non-material)%20consequences%20for%20the%20parties%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20the%20Madras%20high%20court%20held%20that%20a%20wife%20as%20a%20homemaker%20is%20entitled%20to%20an%20equal%20share%20in%20marital%20property%20as%20she%20has%20performed%20household%20chores%20round%20the%20clock%2C%20thereby%20enabling%20the%20husband%20to%20engage%20in%20gainful%20employment%20and%20accumulate%20sufficient%20savings%20to%20purchase%20property.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F37c1e0ee-614f-4025-9b0c-fca3aedfcf73%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F37c1e0ee-614f-4025-9b0c-fca3aedfcf73%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1689733716250000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1j61pY2B9PkOeIOhXjbmF8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20judgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20entirety%20is%20well%20worth%20reading%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F0e735cb7-a956-4065-8898-3335b03499ab%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F0e735cb7-a956-4065-8898-3335b03499ab%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1689733716250000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1e7n4yZ5Rqbohifilq-Nws%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20a%20shorter%20summary%20is%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20societies%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20in%20India%2C%20the%20male%20breadwinner%20and%20female%20caregiver%20model%20is%20deeply%20entrenched.%20This%20social%20expectation%20affects%20women%20and%20girls%20from%20the%20cradle%20to%20the%20grave.%20Admittedly%2C%20men%20suffer%20too%2C%20but%20in%20a%20patriarchal%20society%2C%20women%20are%20much%20worse%20off.%20From%20an%20early%20age%2C%20girls%20are%20socialised%20to%20perform%20well%20in%20the%20reproductive%20economy%20encompassing%20biological%20reproduction%20and%20social%20reproduction%2C%20including%20home%20maintenance%2C%20child%20rearing%2C%20elderly%20care%20and%20transmission%20of%20cultural%20values.%20Men%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20productive%20economy%20and%20put%20bread%20on%20the%20table%20for%20their%20spouses%2C%20children%20and%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20gendered%20social%20contract%20translates%20into%20structural%20inequalities%20that%20largely%20impact%20women%20far%20more%20negatively%20than%20they%20do%20men.%20Fewer%20resources%20are%20invested%20in%20girls%20in%20terms%20of%20education%20and%20health.%20Investment%20in%20women%20is%20not%20approached%20through%20a%20lens%20of%20social%20and%20economic%20equality%2C%20but%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20families%20and%20communities%20which%20will%20thrive%20with%20healthy%20and%20educated%20women%20in%20their%20midst.%20Given%20women%E2%80%99s%20reproductive%20responsibilities%2C%20their%20participation%20in%20the%20productive%20economy%20remains%20low.%20Women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20and%20contribution%20to%20the%20reproductive%20economy%20remains%20invisible%2C%20taken%20for%20granted%2C%20and%20euphemistically%20termed%20%E2%80%98priceless%E2%80%99%20when%20any%20attempt%20is%20made%20to%20value%20this%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgement%20correctly%20points%20out%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20reproductive%20labour%20%E2%80%9Cfrees%20her%20husband%20for%20his%20economic%20activities%E2%80%9D.%20Thus%2C%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20economic%20justice%2C%20both%20spouses%20should%20be%20the%20legal%20owners%20of%20property%20and%20other%20assets%20acquired%20during%20marriage.%20This%20can%20be%20achieved%20by%20a%20gender%20egalitarian%20marital%20regime%20(rules%20governing%20the%20ownership%20and%20management%20of%20property%20during%20marriage%20and%20upon%20its%20dissolution).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBroadly%2C%20there%20are%20community%20property%20and%20separation%20of%20property%20regimes.%20In%20community%20property%2C%20all%20assets%20acquired%20during%20marriage%20are%20treated%20as%20belonging%20to%20both%20spouses.%20Assets%20acquired%20prior%20to%20marriage%20or%20inheritances%20received%20is%20considered%20individually%20owned%20in%20partial%20community%2C%20whereas%20in%20full%20community%2C%20such%20assets%20are%20also%20jointly%20owned.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20separation%20of%20property%20marital%20regime%20treats%20all%20property%20irrespective%20of%20the%20time%20of%20acquisition%2C%20as%20individually%20owned%20property.%20Thus%2C%20community%20of%20property%20recognises%20women%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20marital%20assets%20via%20their%20reproductive%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunity%20of%20property%20is%20of%20great%20relevance%20in%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20where%20women%E2%80%99s%20avenues%20for%20asset%20acquisition%20are%20limited.%20Women%20do%20not%20typically%20inherit%20from%20their%20parents%20and%20due%20to%20their%20low%20labour%20force%20participation%2C%20often%20lack%20sufficient%20earnings%20to%20purchase%20property%20and%20other%20high-value%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20by%20Deere%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eet%20al%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(2013)%20across%20different%20marital%20regimes%20found%20that%20separation%20of%20property%20regime%20is%20disadvantageous%20to%20married%20women%20(Ghana%20and%20Karnataka)%20compared%20to%20partial%20community%20property%20(Ecuador).%20This%20is%20confirmed%20with%20recent%20data%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Debt%20and%20Investment%20Survey%20(2019)%20which%20for%20the%20first-time%20included%20information%20on%20ownership%20of%20land%20by%20individuals%20within%20a%20household.%20Unfortunately%2C%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20marital%20status%20is%20not%20collected.%20Our%20analysis%20shows%20that%20only%207%25%20of%20married%20women%20own%20land%20in%20landed%20households.%20The%20comparable%20number%20is%2093%25%20for%20currently%20single%20women.%20Presumably%2C%20the%20currently%20single%20category%20is%20largely%20comprised%20of%20widows%20who%20inherit%20their%20husband%E2%80%99s%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20society%20should%20not%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20enlightened%20judgements%20to%20realise%20the%20goal%20of%20gender%20equality%20that%20is%20promised%20under%20our%20Constitution.%20We%20urgently%20need%20laws%20to%20deliver%20on%20this%20promise%20so%20that%20all%20married%20women%20have%20rights%20and%20entitlements%20within%20marriage%20without%20having%20to%20approach%20the%20court%20for%20redress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHema%20Swaminathan%20and%20Supriya%20Lakhtakia%20are%20at%20IIM%20Bangalore%2C%20Rahul%20Lahoti%20is%20at%20the%20UN%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689673879000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F25151359%2FIMG_3857.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fwomen-family-property-inheritence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Analysis%20shows%20that%20only%207%25%20of%20married%20women%20own%20land%20in%20landed%20households.%20The%20comparable%20number%20is%2093%25%