eport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F07203609%2F16074325569_e1a64acf2f_o.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Barclays%20Plc%2C%20one%20of%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%2012%20%E2%80%98core%20relationship%20banks%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20re-evaluating%20its%20ties%20with%20the%20Indian%20conglomerate%20as%20a%20fallout%20of%20the%20American%20short%20seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%20that%20came%20out%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fgautam-adanis-go-to-bankers-at-barclays-turn-cautious-after-hindenburg-report%2Farticleshow%2F101841746.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20Research%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwhy-has-the-adani-hindenburg-issue-become-a-matter-of-national-concern%5C%22%3Eflagged%3C%2Fa%3E%20Adani%20group%E2%80%99s%20improper%20use%20of%20tax%20havens%20and%20concerning%20debt%20levels%20among%20other%20malpractices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBloomberg%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20citing%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%2C%20said%20that%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20top%20executives%20are%20scrutinising%20ties%20with%20Adani%20and%20are%20cautious%20of%20taking%20up%20new%20deals%20while%20a%20regulatory%20probe%20on%20the%20group%20is%20still%20on.%20The%20bank%20has%20renegotiated%20repayment%20on%20some%20loans%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarclays%E2%80%99%20revenue%20from%20Asia%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20in%20the%20last%20six%20years%2C%20with%20India%20leading%20the%20way%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20tough%20choice%20since%20Adani%20may%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20a%20winner%20and%20the%20banks%20certainly%20want%20to%20be%20associated%