20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-group-trying-to-sell-stake-in-ambuja-cement-to-reduce-debt-report%5C%22%3Ehelped%3C%2Fa%3E%20finance%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20%246.5%20billion%20deal%20to%20buy%20Holcim%E2%80%99s%20cement%20assets%20in%20India%2C%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20takeover%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarclays%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctrusted%20sounding%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20Holcim%20purchase%2C%20providing%20part%20of%20the%20financing%20as%20well%20as%20merger%20advice%2C%20Jugeshinder%20Singh%2C%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20chief%20financial%20officer%2C%20had%20said%20in%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finfra.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fconstruction%2Fadanis-go-to-bankers-at-barclays-turn-cautious-after-hindenburg%2F101851300%5C%22%3E%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20now%20renegotiated%20repayment%20on%20loans%20pertaining%20to%20the%20massive%20cement%20deal%2C%3Cem%3E%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarclays%20was%20also%20not%20part%20of%20the%20recent%20lending%20group%20for%20Adani%2C%20which%20included%20ING%20Bank%20NV%2C%20Mizuho%20Bank%2C%20MUFG%20Bank%2C%20Natixis%20SA%2C%20Standard%20Chartered%20Plc%2C%20and%20Sumitomo%20Mitsui%20Banking%20Corp%2C%20financing%20a%20data%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20on%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20addressing%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20Annual%20General%20Meeting%20(AGM)%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20July%2018%2C%20Adani%20said%20the%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%20against%20the%20conglomerate%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20damage%20its%20image%2C%20news%20agency%20ANI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fsc-panel-report-helped-rebuild-confidence-in-group-gautam-adani-on-malicious-hindenburg-allegations%2F1674659%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fsc-panel-report-helped-rebuild-confidence-in-group-gautam-adani-on-malicious-hindenburg-allegations%2F1674659%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20report%20%E2%80%98a%20deliberate%20and%20malicious%20attempt%20aimed%20at%20damaging%20our%20reputation%20and%20generating%20a%20profit%20by%20driving%20down%20its%20stock%20prices%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20Research%20had%20shorted%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20stocks%20just%20before%20its%20launch%20of%20the%20largest%20follow-on%20public%20offering%20(FPO)%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20history.%20After%20the%20report%20was%20published%2C%20Adani%20Enterprises%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-calls-of-fpo-sebi%5C%22%3Ehad%20to%20call%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Rs%2020%2C000-crore%20FPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fv%5C%22%3Eemphasised%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20expert%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20had%20helped%20rebuild%20confidence%20in%20the%20Adani%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20(SC-constituted)%20expert%20committee%20did%20not%20find%20any%20regulatory%20failure.%20The%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20not%20only%20observed%20that%20the%20mitigating%20measures%20undertaken%20by%20your%20company%20(Adani%20Group)%20helped%20rebuilt%20confidence%20but%20also%20cited%20that%20there%20were%20credible%20charges%20of%20targetted%20destablisation%20of%20Indian%20markets%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gautam%20Adani%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fsc-panel-report-helped-rebuild-confidence-in-group-gautam-adani-on-malicious-hindenburg-allegations%2F1674659%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20investors%20at%20the%20AGM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20expert%20committee%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbecause-of-repealed-provisions-sebi-hit-opaque-structure-wall-while-investigating-adani-sc-panel%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20because%20of%20some%20repealed%20provisions%20in%202018%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20hit%20a%20wall%20in%20investigating%20the%20offshore%20dealings%20of%20the%20Adani%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expert%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20released%20in%20May%2C%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%202018%2C%20the%20provision%20of%20dealing%20with%20an%20%E2%80%98opaque%20structure%E2%80%99%20and%20requiring%20an%20FPI%20to%20disclose%20every%20ultimate%20natural%20person%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20chain%20of%20every%20owner%20of%20economic%20interest%20with%20the%20FPI%20was%20done%20away%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20report%20added%20that%20the%20markets%20regulator%20suspects%20wrongdoing%2C%20but%20also%20finds%20compliance%20with%20various%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsebi-adani-probe-extension-supreme-court%5C%22%3Ehas%20granted%3C%2Fa%3E%20SEBI%20time%20till%20August%2014%20to%20investigate%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689673538000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F07203609%2F16074325569_e1a64acf2f_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fbarclays-adani-group-deals-hindenburg-research%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Barclays%20is%20one%20of%20Adani%20group%E2%80%99s%2012%20%E2%80%99core%20relationship%20banks%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20going%20back%20to%20more%20than%20a%20decade.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fbarclays-adani-group-deals-hindenburg-research%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22tit