oved%20the%20apex%20court%20against%20the%20order%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20heard%20its%20plea%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiveLaw%20has%20reported%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20granted%20liberty%20to%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20approach%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2015%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-internet-ban-supreme-court%5C%22%3Eextended%3C%2Fa%3E%20what%20was%20then%20a%2073-day%20internet%20ban%20on%20the%20state%20till%203%20pm%20on%20July%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20rumour%20is%20likely%20to%20ignite%20riots.%20The%20question%20of%20internet%20is%20sometimes%20open%20and%20then%20sometimes%20it%20is%20not.%20My%20prayer%20is%20that%20the%20Internet%20issue%20can%20be%20left%20to%20the%20discretion%20of%20those%20on%20ground%2C%20my%20lord%2C%E2%80%9D%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%2C%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20said.%20SG%20Mehta%20was%20appearing%20for%20the%20Manipur%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20CJI%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justice%20P.S.%20Narasimha%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%20said%20that%20the%20government%20will%20approach%20the%20high%20court%20on%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20difficulties%20faced%20in%20implementing%20its%20order%20regarding%20internet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689668571000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F25174440%2Fimage-1084.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-violence-strike-bandh-internet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20refused%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court's%20order%20which%20directed%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20partially%20restore%20internet%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20without%20services%20for%20close%20to%2080%20days%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engage