sheet%20against%20Singh%20(which%20it%20did%2C%20on%20June%2015)%20and%20that%20fresh%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20to%20select%20leadership%20for%20the%20federation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20scheduled%20for%20July%2011%2C%20this%20election%20was%20initially%20stayed%20by%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20after%20the%20Assam%20Wrestling%20Association%20(AWA)%20sought%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20electoral%20college%20as%20a%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20WFI.%20The%20high%20court%2C%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20said%20that%20the%20next%20hearing%20would%20be%20on%20July%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20now%20the%20Tripura%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20WFI%20%E2%80%93%20Wrestling%20Association%20of%20Tripura%20%E2%80%93%20has%20also%20petitioned%20the%20high%20court%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20electors%E2%80%99%20list%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiveLawIndia%2Fstatus%2F1680933180394594305%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20outlet%20has%20it%20that%20eight%20other%20state%20units%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20Tripura%20and%20Assam%20have%20written%20to%20the%20ad%20hoc%20panel%20over%20WFI%20%E2%80%98illegally%20disaffiliating%E2%80%99%20state%20bodies.%20This%20disaffiliation%20process%20took%20place%20during%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%2012-year%20term%20as%20president%20of%20the%20body%2C%20the%20state%20bodies%20have%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20state%20units%20alleged%20that%20Singh%20used%20his%20influence%20to%20place%20family%20members%20and%20his%20own%20people%20in%20state%20bodies%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20earlier%20letter%20to%20the%20ad%20hoc%20committee%20on%20May%205%2C%20the%20Tripura%20wrestling%20body%20president%20Rupak%20Deb%20Roy%20said%20Brij%20Bhushan%20had%20told%20him%20to%20%E2%80%9Csend%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20name%20from%20Tripura%20for%20the%202015%20WFI%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20elections%20are%20being%20conducted%20by%20an%20ad-hoc%20committee%20set%20up%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20complaints%20against%20Brij%20Bhushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20World%20Wrestling%20(UWW)%2C%20the%20international%20governing%20body%20for%20amateur%20wrestling%2C%20had%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F655711%2Fuww-protesting-wrestlers-statement%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20failure%20to%20uphold%20the%20deadline%20for%20election%20to%20the%20WFI%20%E2%80%9Cmay%20lead%20UWW%20to%20suspend%20the%20federation%2C%20thereby%20forcing%20the%20athletes%20to%20compete%20under%20a%20neutral%20flag.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689659123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F28101552%2FIMG_1191.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwrestling-federation-of-india-elections-face-further-delay%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20Assam%20Wrestling%20Association%20sought%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20electoral%20college%2C%20the%20Tripura%20state%20wing%20has%20also%20moved%20court%20with%20a%20similar%20plea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwrestling-federation-of-india-elections-face-further-delay%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Arrests%20Despite%20FIR%20Against%20Policemen%20and%20Inquiry%20Report%20in%20MP%20Custodial%20Death%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30123722%2FIllustration-Pariplab-Chakraborty.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGuna%20(Madhya%20Pradesh)%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20March%202023%2C%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20in%20the%20Cantt%20police%20station%20against%20four%20policemen%20and%20a%20civilian%20in%20allegations%20of%20the%20custodial%20killing%20of%20a%20Muslim%20man%20in%20November%202022%20in%20the%20Guna%20district%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20Khan%2C%20a%20daily-wage%20labourer%2C%20was%20detained%20by%20the%20police%20while%20he%20was%20returning%20home%20after%20attending%20a%20three-day%20religious%20congregation%20in%20Bhopal.%20A%20magistrate%20inquiry%20was%20immediately%20ordered%20following%20protests%20by%20locals%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FIR%20came%20three%20months%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20yet%20none%20of%20the%20accused%20have%20been%20arrested.%20Israel%20was%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20three%20daughters%20and%20one-year-old%20son.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Findia%2F2022%2F11%2F22%2F30-year-old-man-dies-in-police-custody-in-guna-third-incident-in-mp-in-3-months.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethird%20instance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20custodial%20death%20in%20the%20state%20within%20three%20months.%20According%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Fcyber-crime%2F88-custodial-deaths-in-india-gujarat-highest-for-second-year-national-crime-records-bureau-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20data%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20India%20reported%2088%20custodial%20deaths%20in%202021%2C%20with%20Gujarat%20on%20top%20with%2023%20custodial%20deaths%2C%20followed%20by%20Maharashtra%20with%2021%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20with%20seven.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20an%20increase%20of%2013.6%25%20in%20custodial%20deaths%20in%20comparison%20to%202020%2C%20which%20reported%2076%20custodial%20deaths.%201%2C888%20custodial%20deaths%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fcustodial-deaths-india-policemen-convicted-ncrb-data-altaf-case-1877539-2021-11-17%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehave%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20India%20over%20the%20last%2020%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManohar%20Mirota%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20advocate%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20report%20of%20the%20magisterial%20inquiry%20has%20been%20recently%20released%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(SP)%20and%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20in%20Bhopal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20our%20applications%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20given%20to%20us.%20Immediate%20police%20action%20was%20required%20given%20the%20grave%20circumstances%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20yet%20nobody%20has%20been%20arrested%20after%20three%20months%20of%20registering%20the%20FIR%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirota%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Guna%20Police%20has%20failed%20in%20taking%20action%20because%20the%20accused%20belong%20to%20the%20police%20department.%20They%20have%20not%20even%20arrested%20the%20civilian%20who%20is%20in%20fact%20threatening%20the%20family.%20The%20SP%20told%20us%20nothing%20about%20the%20magisterial%20inquiry%20report.%20It%20is%20sidelined%3B%20however%2C%20we%20suspect%20that%20the%20town%20inspector%20could%20have%20been%20named%20in%20it%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20in%20a%20hurry%20before%20the%20report%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcustodial-death-uttar-pradesh%5C%22%3EBehind%20India%E2%80%99s%20Custodial%20Death%20Numbers%20Are%20%E2%80%98Brazenly%20Ignored%E2%80%99%20Guidelines%2C%20Say%20Experts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20exactly%20happened%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%2065-year-old%20Munawwar%20Khan%2C%20the%20incident%20happened%20at%208%20pm%20on%20November%2021%2C%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20Israel%20was%20on%20a%20call%20with%20his%20mother-in-law%20when%20four%20policemen%20stopped%20the%20auto-rickshaw%20in%20which%20he%20was%20returning%20and%20detained%20him%20at%20the%20Kushmuda%20police%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echowki%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20His%20family%20was%20informed%20of%20the%20incident%20by%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20mother-in-law.%20Along%20with%20a%20few%20locals%2C%20Munawwar%20reached%20the%20chowki%2C%20where%20they%20could%20hear%20the%20merciless%20beating%20of%20his%20son.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20groaning%20in%20pain.%20We%20could%20hear%20his%20painful%20screams%20outside%20the%20chowki.%20I%20pleaded%20with%20the%20policemen%20to%20let%20go%20of%20my%20son%20and%20said%20I%20will%20pay%20them%20with%20whatever%20they%20wanted.%20They%20thrashed%20us%20when%20we%20tried%20to%20enter%20the%20chowki%2C%20and%20then%20my%20son%20was%20silent%20after%2015%20minutes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Munawwar%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20at%20peace%20that%20he%20stopped%20screaming%20because%20%5Bwe%20thought%5D%20there%20was%20no%20more%20beating.%20We%20were%20confident%20that%20they%20would%20not%20beat%20him%20to%20death%20as%20he%20was%20innocent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20policemen%20at%20the%20chowki%20asked%20Munawwar%20and%20two%20other%20men%20present%20with%20him%20to%20reach%20the%20Cantt%20police%20station%2C%20as%20they%20were%20taking%20Israel%20there.%20Khan%20and%20the%20men%20reached%20the%20police%20station%20and%20waited%20there%20for%20at%20least%2045%20minutes%2C%20when%20they%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20Kushmuda%20chowki%20to%20reach%20the%20hospital%20where%20they%20had%20taken%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98He%20is%20doing%20a%20drama.%20We%20are%20taking%20him%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20medical%20checkup%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20policeman%20on%20call%20had%20said.%20My%20son%E2%80%99s%20body%20was%20lying%20on%20the%20stretcher%20when%20we%20reached%20the%20hospital.%20He%20was%20dead%20already%20and%20the%20police%20were%20not%20present%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Munawwar%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMirota%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%2C%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20was%20forcefully%20taking%20his%20body%20from%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20pressuring%20the%20family%20for%20burial%2C%20but%20we%20urged%20them%20for%20a%20post-mortem.%20The%20post-mortem%20report%20said%20that%20Israel%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%20%E2%80%93%20which%20led%20to%20the%20protest%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police%20assured%20us%20of%20a%20magistrate%20inquiry.%20Twenty-three%20witnesses%20gave%20their%20statements%20in%20front%20of%20the%20magistrate%20on%20the%20same%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMirota%20further%20added%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20viscera%20report%20revealed%20that%20he%20died%20of%20cardiorespiratory%20failure%20and%20a%20head%20injury.%20Following%20the%20report%2C%20an%20FIR%20(0185%2F2023)%20was%20registered%20on%20March%205%20against%20three%20police%20constables%2C%20a%20home%20guard%20and%20one%20other%20individual%20under%20Sections%20302%20(murder)%20and%2034%20(involvement%20of%20two%20or%20more%20persons%20in%20crime)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20names%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR%20are%20Ravindra%20Solanki%2C%20Shivkumar%20Raghuvanshi%2C%20Pran%20Singh%2C%20Lakhan%20Jatav%20and%20civilian%20Saddam%20Khan.%20Four%20policemen%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20have%20been%20line%20attached%20(transferred)%20since%20the%20date%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15153128%2FMarch-2023-FIR-1024x512.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15153128%2FMarch-2023-FIR-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15153128%2FMarch-2023-FIR-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15153128%2FMarch-2023-FIR-800x400.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15153128%2FMarch-2023-FIR.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663346%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20March%202023%20FIR%20filed%20against%20four%20policemen%20and%20one%20civilian.%20Photo%3A%20Huneza%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMirota%20alleged%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20family%20has%20been%20under%20political%20pressure%20to%20withdraw%20their%20complaint%20since%20they%20made%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20I%20was%20lured%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20case.%20Saddam%20Khan%2C%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20is%20a%20police%20agent.%20It%20is%20his%20business%20to%20spy%20upon%20people%20and%20trap%20them%20into%20false%20charges%20for%20making%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirota%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Cantt%20police%20station%20denied%20allegations%20of%20death%20threats%20to%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Findia%2F2022%2F11%2F22%2F30-year-old-man-dies-in-police-custody-in-guna-third-incident-in-mp-in-3-months.html%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Findia%2F2022%2F11%2F22%2F30-year-old-man-dies-in-police-custody-in-guna-third-incident-in-mp-in-3-months.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1689653669863000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3q-Lwk_nXpu6AbzWBgEs9c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20report%20by%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Week%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0last%20year%20said%20that%20Israel%20was%C2%A0reportedly%C2%A0part%20of%20a%20group%20of%20people%20that%20had%20a%20confrontation%20with%20local%20police%20while%20attempting%20to%20save%20a%20gambler%20who%20tried%20to%20escape%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20reportedly%20detained%20and%20questioned%20by%20the%20police%20over%20the%20same%20and%20allegedly%20died%20in%20their%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMaktoob%20Media%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0also%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaktoobmedia.com%2Ffeatures%2Fmuslim-man-found-dead-after-police-detention-family-alleges-cops-rss-men-killed-him%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fmaktoobmedia.com%2Ffeatures%2Fmuslim-man-found-dead-after-police-detention-family-alleges-cops-rss-men-killed-him%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1689653669863000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1SfyWARzeRFxeoU4LMxRDZ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20then-SP%20of%20Guna%20Police%20said%20a%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20Israel%20on%20November%2018%2C%202022.%20Its%20report%20said%20a%20group%20of%20six%20people%20playing%20cardsgot%20into%20a%20verbal%20confrontation%20with%20local%20police%20that%20same%20day%20while%20Israel%20was%20sitting%20near%20them%2C%20and%20quoted%20the%20SP%20as%20saying%20that%20Israel%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20relation%20to%20this%20case%20when%20his%20condition%20deteriorated%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20father%20denied%20these%20allegations.%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%20accessed%20a%20copy%20of%20an%20FIR%20(0888%2F2022)%20filed%20by%20the%20Guna%20Police%20on%20November%2018%20against%20six%20individuals%20who%20allegedly%20asked%20a%20man%20for%20gambling%20money%20and%20then%20assaulted%20him.%20The%20individuals%20named%20are%20Saleem%20Khan%2C%20Khaleel%20Khan%2C%20Altaf%20Khan%2C%20Shahid%20Khan%2C%20Ibrahim%20Khan%20and%20Afsar%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15153652%2FNovember-2022-FIR-1024x512.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15153652%2FNovember-2022-FIR-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15153652%2FNovember-2022-FIR-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15153652%2FNovember-2022-FIR-800x400.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15153652%2FNovember-2022-FIR.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663348%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20FIR%20filed%20in%20November%202022%20in%20the%20gambling%20case.%20Photo%3A%20Huneza%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20not%20mentioned%20in%20that%20FIR.%20Mirota%20said%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20added%20to%20the%20FIR%20after%20he%20died%20to%20cover%20up%20his%20death.%20Notably%2C%20the%20said%20FIR%20was%20filed%20by%20complainant%20Saddam%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20alleged%20custodial%20killing%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20family%E2%80%99s%20plight%3A%20No%20government%20aid%20provided%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReena%20Bano%2C%2030%2C%20is%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20widow.%20She%20is%20devastated%20by%20the%20death%20of%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20was%20innocent.%20He%20was%20on%20a%20phone%20call%20with%20my%20mother%20when%20the%20policemen%20held%20him.%20He%20was%20the%20sole%20breadwinner%20of%20the%20family.%20His%20death%20has%20led%20us%20to%20live%20on%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20mercy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20administration%20didn%E2%80%99t%20provide%20us%20with%20any%20aid.%20I%20have%20become%20lonely.%20My%20children%20are%20helpless%20without%20their%20father%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%20continued%2C%20breaking%20into%20tears.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20thought%20of%20the%20old%20days%20made%20Bano%20nostalgic.%20She%20said%20they%20were%20a%20happy%20family%20living%20together%20in%20harmony%20without%20any%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20grief%20surrounding%20us.%20We%20are%20helpless%20even%20for%20food.%20My%20children%20cry%20for%20their%20father.%20They%20ask%20questions%2C%20%E2%80%98Do%20we%20deserve%20to%20live%20in%20this%20poor%20condition%3F%E2%80%99%20We%20are%20living%20in%20fear.%20They%20killed%20my%20innocent%20husband.%20They%20might%20kill%20us%20for%20not%20signing%20a%20compromise.%20I%20only%20want%20justice%20for%20my%20husband%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fstruggles-widows-men-custodial-death-uttar-pradesh%5C%22%3EThe%20Struggles%20of%20Widows%20of%20Men%20Who%20Died%20in%20Custody%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20her%20in-laws%20have%20been%20receiving%20death%20threats%20from%20the%20start.%20She%20demands%20a%20job%20from%20the%20administration%20to%20compensate%20for%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20murder.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20give%20a%20good%20education%20to%20my%20children%20and%20take%20care%20of%20my%20in-laws.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20independent%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMunawwar%20is%20struggling%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20his%20family.%20Calamities%20are%20no%20stranger%20to%20him%20%E2%80%93%20he%20lost%20his%20elder%20son%20and%20now%20another%20of%20his%20sons%20met%20with%20a%20brutal%20accident%20while%20searching%20for%20livelihood.%20Bedridden%2C%20his%20voice%20cracked%20as%20he%20narrated%20his%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIsrael%20used%20to%20run%20the%20family.%20We%20are%20very%20poor%20now.%20We%20get%20food%20for%20the%20morning%20and%20have%20no%20hopes%20for%20the%20evening%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20son%20was%20innocent%20and%20there%20are%20no%20criminal%20records%20in%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20his%20family%20was%20put%20under%20political%20pressure%20to%20take%20their%20complaint%20back.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20prefer%20dying%20to%20compromising%20in%20this%20situation.%20I%20only%20want%20justice%20for%20my%20son%20and%20his%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15154454%2FChildren-and-father-of-Israel-Khan.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15154454%2FChildren-and-father-of-Israel-Khan.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15154454%2FChildren-and-father-of-Israel-Khan-300x165.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663350%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22352%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMunawwar%20Khan%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20four%20children.%20Photo%3A%20Huneza%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGuna%20superintendent%20of%20police%20Rakesh%20Sagar%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20in%20the%20case%20but%20the%20accused%20have%20not%20been%20arrested%20due%20to%20some%20new%20facts%20coming%20to%20light.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20accepted%20in%20the%20inquiry%20report%20that%20the%20man%20died%20in%20police%20custody.%20The%20CSP%20%5Bchief%20superintendent%20of%20police%5D%20was%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20but%20as%20per%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20inquiry%20report%2C%20we%20have%20handed%20over%20the%20diary%20to%20SDPO%20%5BSub-Divisional%20Police%20Officer%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sagar%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20proper%20investigation%20is%20done%20when%20a%20case%20is%20registered%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20the%20accused%20committed%20the%20crime%20or%20not.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20report%20was%20released%20recently.%20We%20will%20try%20to%20wind%20up%20the%20case%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESDPO%20Vivek%20Asthana%20said%20that%20the%20FIR%20was%20registered%20before%20the%20magisterial%20inquiry%20report%2C%20which%20lies%20with%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20diary%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20me%20recently.%20We%20are%20investigating%20the%20case%20and%20even%20took%20statements%20from%20key%20witnesses%20a%20few%20days%20back.%20The%20witnesses%20haven%E2%80%99t%20informed%20me%20about%20any%20threats.%20If%20there%20is%20any%20such%20thing%2C%20then%20they%20may%20register%20a%20separate%20FIR%20with%20the%20Cantt%20police%20station%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asthana%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CSP%20investigated%20the%20case%20and%20registered%20an%20FIR%2C%20and%20the%20case%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20me%20later.%20We%20will%20try%20to%20resolve%20it%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDelaying%20an%20FIR%20is%20criminal%20neglect%3A%20Ex-bureaucrat%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEx-bureaucrat%20Swaran%20Ram%20Darapuri%20said%20that%20an%20immediate%20FIR%20is%20mandatory%20in%20the%20case%20of%20custodial%20killing%2C%20which%20was%20not%20done%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20case.%20He%20added%20that%20delaying%20this%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20and%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20orders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20criminal%20neglect%20to%20delay%20the%20FIR%20for%20three%20months.%20The%20supervising%20authorities%20should%20also%20be%20held%20liable%20along%20with%20the%20perpetrators%2C%20as%20they%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20jurisdiction%20within%20their%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20Darapuri%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20threats%20against%20family%20and%20witnesses%20are%20obvious.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20must%20ensure%20that%20there%20should%20not%20be%20any%20undue%20pressure%20or%20threats%20against%20them.%20Those%20who%20are%20accused%20are%20not%20enough%2C%20because%20nothing%20goes%20without%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20SHO.%20He%20