pg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323617%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManzilat%20runs%20a%20home%20diner%20that%20keeps%20a%20number%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20keep%20the%20legacy%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive%2C%20she%20set%20up%20Manzilat%E2%80%99s%20home%20diner%20in%20Kasba%20of%20Kolkata%20in%202018.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20nawabs%20were%20very%20fond%20of%20food%20and%20Awadhi%20cuisine%20is%20very%20popular%20but%20not%20so%20popular%20outside%20Lucknow.%20People%20even%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20Metiabruz%20do%20not%20know%20the%20history%20associated%20with%20the%20food.%20I%20wanted%20to%20contribute%20towards%20carrying%20the%20legacy%20of%20my%20family%20before%20the%20world%20forgets%20our%20lineage%20and%20the%20relevance%20of%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManzilat%20manages%20her%20home%20diner%20with%20the%20help%20of%20four%20workers%20and%20caters%20to%20foodies%20from%20across%20the%20world%2C%20including%20Japan%2C%20China%2C%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20Toronto%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mission%20is%20not%20to%20earn%20from%20a%20commercial%20set%20up%2C%20but%20to%20spread%20awareness%20on%20the%20history%20of%20Awadh%2C%20its%20last%20King%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah%2C%20freedom%20fighter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F156185%2Fbegum-hazrat-mahal-british-1857-mutiny%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBegum%20Hazrat%20Mahal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20our%20family%20history.%20For%20this%2C%20I%20get%20immense%20love%2C%20honour%2C%20and%20respect%2C%20which%20is%20priceless.%20That%20is%20my%20real%20earning%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689227864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http