20architecture%20of%20the%20building%20complements%20and%20blends%20into%20the%20greenery%20on%20the%20grounds%2C%20the%20building%20materials%20sing%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CPreserving%20the%20existing%20nature%20was%20one%20of%20our%20first%20goals%20while%20designing%20the%20property.%20There%20were%20fruit%20trees%20such%20as%20mango%20and%20jamun%2C%20which%20are%20still%20growing%20on%20the%20grounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20materials%2C%20the%20duo%20tried%20to%20upcycle%2C%20recycle%20and%20reduce%20waste%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20architecture%20of%20the%20place%20is%20so%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature%2C%20the%20materials%20had%20to%20be%20too.%20All%20the%20steel%20used%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20building%20is%20upcycled%20and%20locally%20sourced.%20On%20the%20facade%20of%20the%20building%2C%20we%20used%20exposed%20brickwork.%20The%20reason%20was%20that%20it%20is%20fairly%20permanent%20in%20nature%20so%20the%20life%20cycle%20of%20the%20building%20increases.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20keep%20painting%20it%20up%20every%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311532%2Fbengaluru-betweenlines-sustainable-home-breathe-eco-friendly-earth-house-energy-efficient%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20idea%20of%20sustainability%20forward%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20school%20is%20a%20zero-waste%20campus%20that%20has%20a%20sewage%20disposal%20system%2C%20and%20harvests%201.5%20lakh%20litres%20of%20rainwater%20besides%20children%20growing%20their%20own%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-168